hadiths[188]{hadithnumber,text}:
5063,"teen hazraat ( Ali-bin abi-Talib , Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-al-Aas aur Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu)) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak beeviyon ke gharon ki taraf aap ki ibadat ke mutaalliq poochhney aaey, jab unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka amal bataya gaya to jaisey unhon-ne usey kam samjha aur kaha ke hamara Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya muqaabla ! aap ki to tamam agli pichhli khataein maaf kar di gaee hain. unmein se aik ne kaha ke aaj se main hamesha raat bhar Namaz padha karunga. doosrey ne kaha ke main hamesha rozey se rahunga aur kabhi naagha nahi honey doonga. teesrey ne kaha ke main aurton se judai ikhtiyar kar loonga aur kabhi nikah nahi karunga. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur unse puchha kya tum ne hi ye baatein kahi hain? sun lo! Allah Taala ki qasam! Allah rabbul-aalameen se main tum sabse zyada darney wala hun. main tum mein sabse zyada parhezgaar hun lekin main agar rozey rakhta hun to iftaar bhi karta hun. Namaz padhta hon (raat mein) aur sota bhi hon aur main aurton se nikah karta hoon. فمن رغب an (an) سنتي فليس مني mere tareeqey se jisne be-raghbatii ki wo mujh mein se nahi hai."
5064,"aur unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se Allah Taala ke us irshaad وإن خفتم أن لا تقسطوا في اليتامى فانكحوا ما طاب لكم من Nisa مثنى وثلاث ورباع فإن خفتم أن لا تعدلوا فواحدة أو ما ملكت أيمانكم ذلك أدنى أن لا تعولواke mutaalliq puchha ''aur agar tumhen andesha ho ke tum yatimon se insaf na kar sakogey to jo auratein tumhen pasand hon unse nikah kar lo. 2-2 se, chahe teen-teen se, chahe chaar-chaar se, lekin agar tumhen andesha ho ke tum insaf nahi kar sakogey to phir aik hi par bas karo ya jo londi tumhari milk mein ho, is sura mein qawii ummeed hai ke tum zulm w zyadti na kar sakogey.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : bhaanjey! aayat mein aisi yateem maaldaar ladki ka zikr hai jo apne wali ki parwarish mein ho. wo ladki ke maal aur uske husn ki wjah se uski taraf maail ho aur us se maamooli mehar par shadi karna chahta ho to aisey shakhs ko is aayat mein aisi ladki se nikah karne se mana kya gaya hai. haan agar iske sath insaf kar sakta ho aur pura mehar ada karne ka irada rakhta ho to ijazat hai, warna aisey logon se kaha gaya hai ke apni parwarish mein yateem ladkiyon ke siwa aur dusri ladkiyon se shadi kar lein."
5065,"mein Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha, unse Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mina mein mulaqat ki aur kaha : aey abu-Abdur-Rehmaan! mujhey aap se aik kaam hai phir wo donon tanhai mein chaley gaey. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! kya aap manzoor karengey ke ham aap ka nikah kisi kunwari ladki se kar dein jo aapko guzrey huey dinon yad dila de. chunkey Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) uski zarurat mehsus nahi kartey they isliye unhon-ne mujhey ishara kya aur kaha : alqama! main jab unki khidmat mein pahuncha to wo keh rahe they ke agar aap ka ye mashwara hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya tha aey naujawaano! tum mein jo bhi shadi ki taqat rakhta ho usey nikah kar lena chahiye kyonke ye khaahishe-nafsaanii ko tod dega."
5066,"main Alqama aur Aswad ( (Rahmatullahi-alaih) (ke sath Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, unhon-ne ham se kaha ke ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein naujawaan they aur hamein koi cheez muyassar nahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya ke naujawaanon ki jamat ! tum mein jisey bhi nikah karne ke liye maalii taqat ho usey nikah kar lena chahiye kyonke ye nazar ko neechi rakhney wala aur sharmgah ki hifazat karne wala amal hai aur jo koi nikah ki ghurbat ki wajah se taqat na rakhta ho usey chahiye ke roza rakhey kyonke roza uski khuwaahishaat nafsaanii ko tod dega."
5067,ham Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Ummul-Momenin Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke janaaze mein Sharik they. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi hain jab tum unka janaaza uthao to zor-zor se harkat na dena balke ahista-ahista narmii ke sath janaaza ko lekar chalnaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aap ki wafat ke waqt aap ke nikah mein nau (9) beeviyan thin aath (8) ke liye to aap ne baari muqarrar kar rakhi thi lekin aik ki baari nahi thi.
5068,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik martaba aik hi raat main apni tamam beeviyon ke paas gaey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas nau (9) beeviyan thin. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke mujh se khaleefa ibne- khayyaat ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Saeed ne bayan kya, unse Qatada ne aur unse Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
5069,tum ne shadi kar li hai? maine arz kya ke nahi. aap (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke shadi kar lo kyonke is ummat ke behtreen shakhs jo they (yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) unki bahut si beeviyan thin. kuch ne yun tarjama kya hai ke is ummat mein achchhey wahi log hain jinki bahut auratein hun.
5070,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke amal ka daro-madar niyat par hai aur har shakhs ko wahi milta hai jiski wo niyat kare. isliye jiski hijrat Allah aur uske rasool ki raza hasil karne ke liye ho, usey Allah aur uske rasool ki raza hasil hogi lekin jiski hijrat duniya hasil karne ki niyat se ya kisi aurat se shadi karne ke irade se ho, uski hijrat usi ke liye hai jiske liye us ne hijrat ki."
5071,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad kya kartey they aur hamarey sath beeviyan nahi thin. isliye ham ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! ham apne aapko khassi kyon na kar lein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein us se mana farmaya,"
5072,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu)) hijrat karke Madeena) aaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke aur Sad-bin-Rabee Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan bhai chaara karaya. Sad Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein 2 beeviyan thin. unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke wo unke ahal ( biwi (aur maal mein se aadha ley lein. is par Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke Allah Taala aap ke ahal aur aap ke maal mein barkat de, mujhey to bazar ka rasta bata do. chunanche aap bazar aaey aur yahan aap ne kuchh paneer aur kuchh ghi ki tijarat ki aur nafa kamaayaa . chand dinon ke baad un par zafran ki zardi lagi hui thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Abdur-Rehman ye kya hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke maine aik Ansari khatun se shadi kar li hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke unhein mehar mein kya diya arz kya ke aik guthli barabar sona diya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir walima kar agarche aik bakri hi ka ho."
5073,"maine Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( تبتل ( yani aurton se alag rehney ki zindagi se mana farmaya tha. agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein ijazat de detey to ham to khassi hi ho jatey."
5074,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ko aurat se alag rehney ki ijazat nahi di thi. agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein uski ijazat de detey to ham bhi apne aapko khassi bana letey.
5075,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad ko jaya kartey they aur hamarey paas rupya na tha (ke ham shadi kar letey) isliye ham ne arz kya ham apne ko khassi kyon na kara lein lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein us se mana farmaya, phir hamein uski ijazat de di ke ham kisi aurat se aik kapdey par (eik muddat tak ke liye) nikah kar lein. aap ne hamein Quran Majeed ki ye aayat padh kar sunaaii يا أيها الذين آمنوا لا تحرموا طيبات ما أحل الله لكم wla تعتدوا إن الله لا يحب المعتدين‏ ke ''emaan laney waalo! wo pakeeza cheezein mat haram karo jo tumharey liye Allah Taala ne halal ki hain aur had se aagey na badho, beshak Allah had se aagey badhney walon ko pasand nahi kartaa.''"
5076,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! main naujawaan hun aur mujhey apne par zina ka khof rehta hai. mere paas koi aisi cheez nahi jis par main kisi aurat se shadi kar loon. aap meri ye baat sun kar khamosh rahe. dobara maine apni yahi baat dohraaii lekin aap us martaba bhi khamosh rahe. teesri baar maine arz kya aap phir bhi khamosh rahe. maine chothi martaba arz kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey abu-Huraira! jo kuchh tum karogey usey (Lauhe-mahfooz mein) likh kar qalam khushk ho chuka hai. chahe ab tum khassi ho jao ya baaz raho. yani khassi hona bekaar mahz hai.
5077,maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! farmaiye agar aap kisi wadi mein utrein aur is mein aik darakht aisa ho jis mein oont char gaey hon aur aik darakht aisa ho jis mein se kuchh bhi na khaya gaya ho to aap apna oont un darakhton mein se kis darakht mein charaaeingey? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us darakht mein jis mein se abhi charaayaa nahi gaya ho. unka ishara is taraf tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke siwa kisi kunwari ladki se nikah nahi kya.
5078,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey Aaisha! mujhey khuwab mein 2 martaba tum dikhai gaiin. aik shakhs ( Jibraeel ( tumhari sura hareer ke aik tukdey mein uthaey huey hai aur kehta hai ke ye aap ki biwi hai maine jo us kapdey ko khola to usmein tum thin. maine khayal kya ke agar ye khuwab Allah ki taraf se hai to wo usey zaroor pura karke rahega.
5079,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jihad se wapas ho rahe they. main apne oont ko, jo sust tha tez chalaney ki koshish kar raha tha. itney mein mere peechhey se aik sawar mujh se aa kar mila aur apna neza mere oont ko chubho diya. iski wjah se mera oont tez chal padaa jaisa ke kisi umda qism ke oont ki chaal tum ne dekhi hogi. achcha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mil gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya jaldi kyon kar rahe ho? maine arz kya abhi meri shadi nai hui hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kunwari se ya bewa se ? maine arz kya ke bewa se. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke kisi kunwari se kyon na ki tum uske sath khel kood kartey aur wo tumharey sath karti. bayan kya ke phir jab ham Madina mein dakhil hone-waale they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thodi der thahar jao aur raat ho jaey tab dakhil ho taake pareshan baalon wali kangha kar ley aur jinke shauhar maujood nahi they wo apne baal saaf kar lein."
5080,maine shadi ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya ke kis se shadi ki hai? maine arz kya ke aik aurat se. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kunwari se kyon na ki ke iske sath tum khel-kood kartey. Maharib ne kaha ke phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ye irshad Amr-bin-Dinar se bayan kya to unhon-ne kaha ke maine Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai. mujh se unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman is tarah bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke tum ne kisi kunwari aurat se shadi kyon na ki ke tum uske sath khel kood kartey aur wo tumharey sath kheltii.
5081,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se shadi ke liye Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke main aap ka bhai hun. (to Aaisha se kaisey nikah karengey) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke Deen aur uski kitab par eman laney ke rishta se tum mere bhai ho aur Aaisha mere liye halal hai.
5082,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke oont par Sawar honey wali) arab) aurton mein behtreen aurat Quraish ki Saleh aurat hoti hai jo apne bachchey se bahut zyada mohabbat karne wali aur apne shauhar ke maal asbaab mein uski bahut umda nigahbaan w nigraan Sabit hoti hai.
5083,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ke paas londi ho wo usey taleem de aur khub achi tarah de, usey adab sikhaaey aur poori koshish aur mehnat ke sath sikhaaey aur uske baad usey aazad karke us se shadi kar ley to usey dohra sawab milta hai aur ahle-kitab mein se jo shakhs bhi apne Nabi par eman rakhta ho aur mujh par eman laey to usey dohra sawab milta hai aur jo ghulam apne aaqa ke huquq bhi ada karta hai aur apne rab ke huquq bhi ada karta hai usey dohra sawab milta hai. Aamir Shabi ne (apne shagird se us hadis ko sunaney ke baad kaha ke baghair kisi mashaqqat aur mehnat ke usey seekh lo. us se pahley taalib ilmon ko us hadis se kam ke liye bhi Madina tak ka safar karna padta tha aur Abu-Bakar ne bayan kya abu-Haseen se, us ne abu-Barda se, us ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ke us shakhs ne baandi ko (nikaah karne ke liye) aazad kar diya aur yahi aazadi iska mehar muqarrar ki."
5084,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, (doosri sanad) ham se Sulaimaan-bin-Harab ne bayan kya, unse Hammad-bin-Zaid ne, unse Ayub sakhtiyan ne, unse Muhammad-bin Sirin ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Ibrahim ki zaban se teen martaba ke siwa kabhi Deen mein jhoot baat nahi niklii. aik martaba aap aik zaalim badshah ki hukumat se guzrey aap ke sath aap ki biwi saara (Alaihissalam) thin. phir pura waqia bayan kya (ke badshah ke saamney) aap ne saara (Alaihissalam) ko apni behan (yani deenii bahan) kaha, phir us badshah ne Saara (Alaihissalam) ko Aajar (Haajira) ko de diya. (bii-bii Saara (Alaihissalam) ne Ibrahim se) kaha ke Allah Taala ne kaafir ke hath ko rok diya aur Aajar ( Hajra ( ko meri khidmat ke liye dilwaa diya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aey aasman ke pani ke beto! yani aey Arab waalo! yahi Hajra (Alaihissalam) tumhari maan hain."
5085,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar aur Madina ke darmyan teen din tak qiyam kya aur yahin Ummul-Momenin Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khilwat ki. phir maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke walima ki musalmanon ko dawat di. is da'wate-waleema mein na to roti thi aur na gosht tha. dastar-khuwaan bichhaaney ka hukm hua aur is par khajoor, paneer aur ghi rakh diya gaya aur yahi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka walima tha. kuchh musalmanon ne puchha ke Safiya ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se hain (yani Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah kya hai) ya londi ki haisiyat se aap ne unke sath khilwat ki hai? is par kuchh logon ne kaha ke agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke liye parde ka intizam farmaein to us se Sabit hoga ke wo ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se hain aur agar unke liye parde ka ehtimaam na karein to us se Sabit hoga ke wo londi ki haisiyat se aap ke sath hain. phir jab kooch karne ka waqt hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye apni sawari par baithney ke liye jagah banai aur unke liye parda daala taake logon ko wo nazar na aaein."
5086,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko aazad kya aur unki aazadi ko unka mehar qarar diya.
5087,"aik aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah! main aap ki khidmat mein apne-aapko aap ke liye waqf karne hazir hui hun. rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nazar utha kar usey dekha. phir aap ne nazar ko neechi kar liya aur phir apna sar jhukaa liya. jab us aurat ne dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke mutaalliq koi faisla nahi farmaya to wo baith gaee. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! agar aapko unse nikah ki zarurat nahi hai to unse mera nikah kar dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas ( mehar ke liye) koi cheez hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi, Allah ki qism , ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke apne ghar jao aur dekho mumkin hai tumhen koi cheez mil jaey. wo gaey aur wapas aagey aur arz kya : Allah ki qism ! maine kuchh nahi paya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar lohey ki aik anguthi bhi mil jaey to ley aao . wo gaey aur wapas aagey aur arz kya : Allah ki qasam, ya Rasulullah! mere paas lohey ki aik anguthi bhi nahi albatta mere paas aik tahmad hai. unhiin (khaatoon ko) usmein se aadha de dijiye. Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unke paas chadar bhi nahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye tumharey us tahmad ka kya karegii. agar tum usey pahnogey to unke liye usmein se kuchh nahi bachega aur agar wo pahan ley to tumharey liye kuchh nahi rahega. iske baad wo sahabi baith gaey. kafi der tak baithey rehney ke baad jab wo khadey huey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha ke wo wapas ja rahe hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein bulwaya jab wo aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumhen Quran Majeed kitna yad hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke falan-falan soortein yad hain. unhon-ne gin kar bataein . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha kya tum inhein baghair dekhey padh saktey ho? unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jao . maine unhein tumharey nikah mein diya. un Suraton ke badley jo tumhen yad hain."
5088,"abu-Huzaifa bin Utba-bin- Rabee bin Abd-Shams ( مہشم ( ne jawan sahaba mein se they jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-badr mein shirkat ki thi. Saalim-bin Maaqil (Raziallahu anhu) ko ley-paalak betaa banaya, aur phir unka nikah apne bhai ki ladki Hinda-binte-Waleed-bin-Utba-bin- Rabee se kar diya. pahley Salim (Raziallahu anhu) aik Ansari khatun ke aazad karda ghulam they lekin Huzefa ne unko apna munh bola betaa banaya tha jaisa ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zaid ko (jo aap hi ke aazad karda ghulam they) apna ley-paalak betaa banaya tha jahiliyat ke zamaney mein ye dastoor tha ke agar koi shakhs kisi ko ley-paalak betaa bana leta to log usey usi ki taraf nisbat karke pukara kartey they aur ley-paalak betaa uski meeraas mein se bhi hissey paata aakhir jab sura Hujuraat mein ye aayat utri ( ادعوهم لآبائهم‏ (ke '' unhein unke haqiqi baapon ki taraf mansub karke pukaaro ''Allah taala ke farman ( ومواليكم‏ ( tak to log unhein unke baapon ki taraf mansub karke pukarney lagey jiske bap ka ilm na hota to usey ( مولى (aur deenii bhai kaha jata. phir Sehla binte- Suhail-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) jo abu-Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi hain Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham to Salim ko apna haqiqi jaisa betaa samajhtey they ab Allah ne jo hukm utara wo aapko malum hai phir aakhir tak hadis bayan ki."
5089,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zabaa binte- Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaey (ye Zuber abdul-Muttalib ke betey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha they) aur unse farmaya shayad tumhara irada Haj ka hai? unhon-ne arz kya : Allah ki qasam! main to apne aapko bimar paatii hun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke phir bhi Haj ka ehram baandh ley. albatta shart laga lena aur ye keh lena ke aey Allah ! main us waqt halal ho jaaungii jab to mujhey (marz ki wjah se) rok lega aur (zaba'a binte- Zuber qureshi (Raziallahu anhu)) Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thin.
5090,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurat se nikah char chizon ki buniyad par kya jata hai uske maal ki wjah se aur uske khaandaanii sharf ki wjah se aur uski khoobsoortii ki wjah se aur uske Deen ki wjah se aur to diindaar aurat se nikah karke kamiyabi hasil kar, agar aisa na karey to terey hathon ko mitti lagegii (yani akheer mein tujh ko nadaamat hogi) ."
5091,"aik sahib (jo maaldaar they) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney se guzrey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne paas maujood sahaba se puchha ke ye kaisa shakhs hai? sahaba ne arz kya ke ye us laaiq hai ke agar ye nikah ka paigham bhejey to us se nikah kya jaey, agar kisi ki sifarish karey to uski sifarish qabool ki jaey, agar koi baat kahey to ghaur se suni jaey. Sehal ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par chup ho rahe. phir aik doosrey sahib guzrey, jo musalmanon ke ghareeb aur mohtaaj logon mein shumaar kiye jatey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke iske mutaalliq tumhara kya khayal hai? sahaba ne arz kya ke ye is qaabil hai ke agar kisi ke yahan nikah ka paigham bhejey to us se nikah na kya jaey agar kisi ki sifarish karey to uski sifarish qabool na ki jaey, agar koi baat kahey to uski baat na suni jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke ye shakhs akelaa pahley shakhs ki tarah duniya bhar se behtar hai."
5092,"unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aayat (وإن خفتم أن لا تقسطوا في اليتامى‏) ''aur agar tumhen khof ho ke yateem ladkiyon ke barey main tum insaf nahi kar sakogey.'' ke mutaalliq sawal kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha mere bhaanjey! is aayat mein us yateem ladki ka hukm bayan hua hai jo apne wali ki parwarish mein ho aur uska wali uski khoobsoortii aur maaldaaii par reejh kar ye chahey ke us se nikah karey lekin uske mehar mein kami karne ka bhi irada ho. aisey wali ko apni zer parwarish yateem ladki se nikah karne se mana kya gaya hai jab wo unka mehar insaf se pura ada karengey agar wo aisa na karein to phir aayat mein aisey waliyon ko hukm diya gaya ke wo apni zere-parwarish yateem ladki ke siwa kisi aur se nikah kar lein. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uske baad sawal kya to Allah Taala ne sura Nisa mein aayat ( ويستفتونك في Nisa ( se ( وترغبون أن تنكحوهن‏ ( tak nazil ki. is aayat mein Allah Taala ne ye hukm diya ke yateem ladkiyan agar khoobsurat aur saahibe-maal hon to unke wali bhi unke sath nikah kar lena chahtey hain, uska khandan pasand kartey hain aur mehar pura ada karke unse nikah kar letey hain. lekin unmein husn ki kami ho aur maal bhi na ho to phir unki taraf raghbat nahi hogi aur wo unhein chhod kar dusri aurton se nikah kar letey hain. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke aayat ka matlab ye hai ke jaisey us waqt yateem ladki ko chhod detey hain jab wo naadaar ho aur khoobsurat na ho aisey hi us waqt bhi chhod dena chahiye jab wo maaldaar aur khoobsurat ho albatta agar uske haq mein insaf karein aur uska mehar pura ada karein tab us se nikah kar saktey hain."
5093,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahoosat aurat mein, ghar main aur ghodey mein ho sakti hai) nahoosat be-barkatii agar ho to unmein ho sakti hai)."
5094,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney nahoosat ka zikr kya gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar nahoosat kisi cheez mein ho to ghar, aurat aur ghodey mein ho sakti hai."
5095,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ( nahoosat ( kisi cheez mein ho to ghodey, aurat aur ghar mein ho sakti hai."
5096,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine apne baad mardon ke liye aurton ke fitne se badh kar nuqsan dene wala aur koi fitna nahi chhoda hai.
5097,"Barira ke sath teen sunnat qaaim hoti hain, unhein aazad kya aur phir ikhtiyar diya gaya (ke agar chaahein to apne pichhley shauhar se apna nikah tod sakti hain) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Bareera (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein) farmaya ke 'walaa' aazad karaaney waley ke sath qaaim hui hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein dakhil huey to aik handi (gosht ki) choolhey par thi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye roti aur ghar ka saalan laya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) choolhey par) handi ( gosht ki) bhi to maine dekhi thi. arz kya gaya ke wo handi us gosht ki thi jo Barira ko sadqe mein mila tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sadqa nahi khaatey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo uske liye sadqa hai aur ab hamarey liye unki taraf se tohfa hai. ham usey kha saktey hain."
5098,"Allah Taala ke irshaad (وإن خفتم أن لا ، Mina تقسطوا في اليتامى) ''aur agar tumhen khof ho ke tum yatimon ke barey mein insaf nahi kar sakogey.'' ke barey mein farmaya ke us se murad yateem ladki hai jo apne wali ki parwarish mein ho. wali us se iske maal ki wjah se shadi kartey aur achi tarah us se sulook na kartey aur na iske maal ke barey mein insaf kartey aisey shakhson ko ye hukm hua ke us yateem ladki se nikah na karein balke iske siwa jo auratein bhalii lagein unse nikah kar lein. 2-2, teen-teen ya chaar-chaar tak ki ijazat hai."
5099,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan tashrif rakhtey they aur aap ne suna ke koi sahib Ummul-Momenin Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein andar aaney ki ijazat chahtey hain. bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ye shakhs aap ke ghar mein aaney ki ijazat chahta hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mera khayal hai ke ye falan shakhs hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke aik doodh ke chacha ka naam liya. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : kya fulaan, jo unke dudh-sharik chacha they, agar zinda hotey to mere yahan aa ja saktey they? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jaisey khoon milney se hurmat hoti hai, waisey hi doodh peeney se bhi hurmat Sabit ho jati hai."
5100,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke aap Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti se nikah kyon nahi kar letey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo mere dudh-sharik bhai ki beti hai. aur Bishr-bin-Umar ne bayan kya, unse Shoba ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Qatada se suna aur unhon-ne isi tarah Jaabir bin Zaid se suna."
5101,"unhon-ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! meri behan ( Abu-Sufiyan ki ladki ( se nikah kar lijiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum usey pasand karogii (ke tumhari saukan behan baney)? maine arz kya ji haan, main to pasand karti hun agar main akelii aap ki biwi hoti to pasand na karti . phir meri behan agar mere sath bhalai mein Sharik ho to main kyonkar na chaahoongii (ghairon se to behan hi achi hai) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya wo mere liye halal nahi hai. Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah! log kehtey hain aap abu-Salma ki beti se jo Umme-Salma ke pet se hai, nikah karne waley hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo meri rubaiba aur meri parwarish mein na hoti (yani meri biwi ki beti na hotii) jab bhi mere liye halal na hoti. wo doosrey rishtey se meri dudh-sharik bhateejii hai, mujh ko aur abu-Salma ke bap ko donon ko Saubiya ne doodh pilaya hai. dekho, aisa mat karo apni betiyon aur bahnon ko mujh se nikah karne ke liye na kaho. Urwa rawi ne kaha soobiya abu-Lahab ki londi thi. abu-Lahab ne usko aazad kar diya tha. (jab us ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paida honey ki khabar abu-Lahab ko di thi) phir us ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko doodh pilaya tha jab abu-Lahab mar gaya to uske kisi azeez ne marney ke baad usko khuwab mein burey haal mein dekha to puchha kya haal hai kya guzrii? wo kehney laga jab se main tum se juda hua hun kabhi aaraam nahi mila magar aik zara sa pani (peer ke din mil jata hai) abu-Lahab ne us gadhey ki taraf ishara kya jo angoothey aur kalima ke ungli ke beech mein hota hai ye bhi us wjah se ke maine soobiya ko aazad kar diya tha."
5102,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif laey to dekha ke unke yahan aik mard betha hua hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey ka rang badal gaya maano ke aap ne usko pasand nahi farmaya Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! ye mere dudh-sharik bhai hain Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya dekho, soch-samajh kar kaho kon tumhara bhai hai."
5103,"abu-Qaees ke bhai Aflah ne unke yahan andar aaney ki ijazat chahi . wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke dudh-sharik chacha they (ye waqia parde ka hukm nazil honey ke baad ka hai Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke) maine unhein andar aaney ki ijazat nahi di phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke sath apne mamley ko bataya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke main unhein andar aaney ki ijazat de dun."
5104,"maine ye hadis khud Aqba se bhi suni hai lekin mujhey Ubaid ke waastey se suni hui hadis zyada yad hai. Aqba bin-Haaris ne bayan kya ke maine aik aurat (umme-Yahyaa bin abi ahaab) se nikah kya. phir aik kali aurat aai aur kehney lagi ke maine tum donon (miyaan beewii) ko doodh pilaya hai. main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke maine fulaanii binte- falan se nikah kya hai. iske baad hamarey yahan aik kali aurat aai aur mujh se kehney lagi ke maine tum donon ko doodh pilaya hai, halanke wo jhooti hai (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Aqba ka ye kehna ke wo jhooti hai na-gawar guzra (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par apna chehra Mubarak pher liya. phir main aap ke samney aaya aur arz kya wo aurat jhooti hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us biwi se ab kaisey nikah reh sakega jabke ye aurat yun kehti hai ke usne tum donon ko doodh pilaya hai, us aurat ko apne se alag kar do. '' ( hadis ke rawi ( Ismail bin-Ulaih ne apni shahadat aur beech ki ungli se ishara karke bataya ke Ayub ne is tarah ishara karke ."
5105,"khoon ki ro se tum par saat (7) rishtey haram hain aur shadi ki wjah se (yani sasuraal ki taraf se) saat (7) rishtey bhii. unhon-ne ye aayat padhii حرمت عليكم أمهاتكم aakhir tak aur Abdullah-bin Jafar bin abii-Taalib ne Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki sahibzadi Zenab aur Ali ki bii-bii (Laila-binte-Mas'ood ( donon se nikah kya, unko jama kya aur Ibne-Sirin ne kaha usmein koi qabahat nahi hai aur imam Hasan Basri ne aik baar to usey makruh kaha phir kehney lagey usmein koi qabahat nahi hai aur Hasan-bin- Hasan-bin-Ali bin abii-Taalib ne apne donon chaachaaon (yani Muhammad-bin Ali aur Amr bin Ali ( ki betiyon ko aik sath mein nikah mein ley liya aur Jaabir bin Zaid Taabai ne usko makruh jaana, is khayal se ke bahnon mein jalaapaa na paida ho magar ye kuchh haram nahi hai kyonke Allah Taala ne farmaya ( وأحل لكم ما وراء ذلكم‏ (ke unke siwa aur sab auratein tum ko halal hain. aur Ikrima ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya ke agar kisi ne apni saalii se zina kya to uski biwi ( saalii ki bahan) is par haram na hogi aur Yahyaa-bin-Qais Kandi se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Shabi aur Jafar se, donon ne kaha agar koi shakhs lawaatat karey aur kisi laundey ke dakhil kar de to ab uski maan se nikah na kare. aur Yahya rawi mashhoor shakhs nahi hai aur na kisi aur ne uske sath ho kar ye riwayat ki hai aur Ikrima ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke agar kisi ne apni saas se zina kya to uski biwi is par haram na hogi aur abu-Nasar ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke haram ho jaeygi aur us rawi abu-nasa ka haal malum nahi. us ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai ya nahi (lekin Abu-Zaraa ne usey qaabile-bharosa kaha hai) aur Imran-bin-Husain aur Jaabir bin Zaid aur Hasan Basri aur kuchh Iraq walon (Imam Sory aur imam abu-Haneefa (rh)) ka yahi qaul hai ke haram ho jaeygi aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha haram na hogi jab tak uski maan (apni khush-daaman) ko zameen se na laga de (yani us se hambistari na karey) aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur Urwa aur Zohri ne uske mutaalliq kaha hai ke agar koi saas se zina karey tab bhi uski beti yani zina karne waley ki biwi is par haram na hogi (usko rakh sakta hai) aur Zohri ne kaha Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke uski joru is par haram na hogi aur ye riwayat munqata' hai."
5106,"maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! aap Abu-Sufiyan ki sahibzadi (Gharra ya darra ya hamna) ko chahtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir main iske sath kya karunga ? maine arz kya ke us se aap nikah kar lein. farmaya kya tum usey pasand karogii? maine arz kya main koi tanha to hun nahi aur main apni behan ke liye ye pasand karti hun ke wo bhi mere sath aap ke talluq mein Sharik ho jaey. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo mere liye halal nahi hai. maine arz kya mujhey malum hua hai ke aap ne ( Zenab se) nikah ka paigham bheja hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Umme-Salma ki ladki ke paas? maine kaha ke ji haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke waah-waah, agar wo meri rubaiba na hoti jab bhi wo mere liye halal na hoti. mujhey aur uske walid abu-Salma ko Soobiya ne doodh pilaya tha. dekho tum aainda mere nikah ke liye apni ladkiyon aur bahnon ko na pesh kya karo aur Lais-bin-Sad ne bhi is hadis ko Hisham se riwayat kya hai is mein abu-Salma ki beti ka naam darra mazkoor hai."
5107,Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri behan ( غرہ ( binte- abi Sufiyan se aap nikah kar lein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aur tumhen bhi pasand hai? maine arz kya ji haan koi main tanha to hun nahi aur meri khahish hai ke aap ki bhalai mein mere sath meri behan bhi Sharik ho jaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye mere liye halal nahi hai. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah ki qism ! is tarah ki baatein sunney mein aati hain ke aap abu-Salma ki sahibzadi darra se nikah karna chahtey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke Umme-Salma ki ladki se? maine kaha ji haan. farmaya Allah ki qism agar wo meri parwarish mein na hoti jab bhi wo mere liye halal nahi thi kyonke wo mere doodh Sharik bhai ki ladki hai. mujhey aur abu-Salma ko soobiya ne doodh pilaya tha. (is liye wo meri doodh Sharik bhateejii ho gai) tum log mere nikah ke liye apni ladkiyon aur bahnon ko na pesh kya karo.
5108,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kisi aisi aurat se nikah karne se mana kya tha jiski phoophii ya khala uske nikah mein ho. aur Dawud bin Aun ne Shabi se bayan kya aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne.
5109,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi aurat ko uski phoophii ya uski khala ke sath nikah mein jama na kya jaey.
5110,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se mana kya hai ke kisi aurat ko uski phoophii ya uski khala ke sath nikah mein jama kya jaey (Zohri ne kaha ke) ham samajhtey hain ke aurat ke bap ki khala bhi (haraam honey mein) usi darje mein hai kyonke (aglii hadis dekhein).
5111,razaat se bhi un tamam rishton ko haram samjho jo khoon ki wjah se haram hotey hain.
5112,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne shighaar se mana farmaya hai. shighaar ye hai ke koi shakhs apni ladki ya behan ka nikah is shart ke sath karey ke wo doosra shakhs apni (betii ya bahan) usko biyaah de aur kuchh mehar na thahrey.
5113,"Khaula binte- hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) un aurton mein se thin jinhoney apne aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye hiba kya tha. is par Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke aik aurat apne aapko kisi mard ke liye hiba kartey sharmaatii nahi. phir jab aayat ( ترجئ من تشاء منهن‏ ( ''aey paighambar ! to apni jis biwi ko chahey peechhey daal de aur jisey chahey apne paas jagah de '' nazil hui to maine kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ab main samjhii Allah Taala jaldi-jaldi aap ki khushi ko pura karta hai. is hadis ko abu-Saeed (Muhammad-bin muslim), muaddab aur Muhammad-bin-Bishr aur Abda bin Sulaiman ne bhi Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kya hai. aik ne doosrey se kuchh zyada mazmoon naql kya hai."
5114,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Memoona (Raziallahu anhu) se) nikah kya aur us waqt aap ehram baandhey huey they.
5115,Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mutaa aur paaltu gadhey ke gosht se jang khaibar ke zamane mein mana farmaya tha.
5116,"unse aurton ke sath nikah mutaa karne ke mutaalliq sawal kya gaya tha to unhon-ne uski ijazat di, phir unke aik ghulam ne unse puchha ke uski ijazat sakht majboorii ya aurton ki kami ya usi jaisi Suraton mein hogii? to Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke haan. (note : ye hurmat se qabl ki baat hai baad mein har haalat mein har shakhs ke liye mutaa haram qarar diya gaya jo qiyamat tak ke liye hai)."
5117,ham aik lashkar mein they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya ke tumhen mutaa karne ki ijazat di gaee hai is liye tum nikah kar saktey ho.
5118,ham aik lashkar mein they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laey aur farmaya ke tumhen mutaa karne ki ijazat di gaee hai is liye tum nikah kar saktey ho.
5119,"jo mard aur aurat mutaa kar lein aur koi muddat mutaiyan na karein to (kam se kam) teen din, teen raat mil kar rahein, phir agar wo teen din se zyada us mutaa ko rakhna chaahein ya khatm karna chaahein to unhein uski ijazat hai (Salma bin Akwa' kehtey hain ke) mujhey malum nahi ye hukm sirf hamarey ( sahaba ( hi ke liye tha ya tamam logon ke liye hai abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( kehtey hain ke khud Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisi riwayat ki jis se malum hota hai ke mutaa ki hillat mansukh hai."
5120,"main Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha aur unke paas unki beti bhi thin. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne aapko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pesh karne ki gharaz se hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aapko meri zarurat hai? is par Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki beti boliin ke wo kaisi be-haya aurat thi. haaye, be-sharmii! haaye be-sharmii! Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha wo tum se behtar thin, unko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf raghbat thi, isliye unhon-ne apne aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pesh kya."
5121,"aik aurat ne apne aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nikah ke liye pesh kya. phir aik sahabi ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! unka nikah mujh se kara dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya tumharey paas ( mehar ke liye) kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mere paas to kuchh bhi nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao aur talash karo, chahe lohey ki aik anguthi hi mil jaey. wo gaey aur wapas aagey aur arz kya ke Allah ki qism ! maine koi cheez nahi paai . mujhey lohey ki anguthi bhi nahi mili , albatta ye mera tahmad mere paas hai iska aadha unhein de dijiye. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unke paas chadar bhi nahi thi. magar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye tumharey us tahmad ka kya karegii, agar ye usey pahan leygii to ye is qadr chhota kapda hai ke phir to tumharey liye usmein se kuchh baqi nahi bachchey ga aur agar tum pahno gey to uske liye kuchh nahi rahega. phir wo sahib baith gaey, der tak baithey rehney ke baad uthey (aur janey lagey) to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein dekha aur bulaayaa, ya unhein bulaya gaya (raawii ko un alfaz mein shak tha) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha ke tumhen Quran kitna yad hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey fulaan, falan soortein yad hain chand soortein unhon-ne ginaaiin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham ne tumharey nikah mein usko us Quran ke badley de diya jo tumhen yad hai."
5122,"jab (unki saahibzaadii) Hafsa binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) (apne shauhar) Khunais bin Huzafa Sehmi ki wafat ki wjah se bewa ho gain aur Khunais Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahabi they aur unki wafat Madina Munawra mein hui thi. umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unke liye Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ko pesh kya. unhon-ne kaha ke main is maamle mein ghaur karunga. maine kuchh dinon tak intizar kya. phir mujh se Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mulaqat ki aur maine kaha ke agar aap pasand karein to main aap ki shadi Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se kar dun Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh rahe aur mujhey koi jawab nahi diya. unki is berukhi se mujhey Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ke maamle se bhi zyada ranj hua. kuchh dinon tak mein khamosh raha. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) se nikah ka paigham bheja aur maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uski shadi kar di. uske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se miley aur kaha ke jab tum ne Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ka mamla mere samney pesh kya tha to mere is par khamosh rehney se tumhen takleef hui hogi ke maine tumhen iska koi jawab nahi diya tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha ke waqei hui thi Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum ne jo kuchh mere samney rakha tha, iska jawab maine sirf is wjah se nahi diya tha ke mere ilm mein tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khud Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ka zikr kya hai aur main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke raaz ko zahir karna nahi chahta tha agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chhod detey to main Hafsa ko apne nikah mein ley aataa."
5123,Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke hamein malum hua hai ke aap darra binte- abi Salma se nikah karne waley hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya main us se iske bawajud nikah kar sakta hun ke (unki maan ( Umme-Salma mere nikah mein pahley hi se maujood hai aur agar main Umme-Salma se nikah na kiye hota jab bhi wo darra mere liye halal nahi thi. kyonke iske walid ( abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu)) mere doodh Sharik bhai they.
5124,Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayat ( فيما عرضتم‏ ( ki tafseer mein kaha ke koi shakhs kisi aisi aurat se jo iddat mein ho kahey ke mera irada nikah ka hai aur meri khahish hai ke mujhey koi nek bakht aurat muyassar aa jaey aur us nikah mein Qasim-bin-Muhammad ne kaha ke (ta'reez ye hai ke) iddat mein aurat se kahey ke tum meri nazar mein bahut achi ho aur mera khayal nikah karne ka hai aur Allah tumhen bhalai pahunchaaeyga ya isi tarah ke jumley kahey aur Ataa-bin-Abii Ribah ne kaha ke ta'reez w kinaaya se kahey. saaf-saaf na kahey (maslan) kahey ke mujhey nikah ki zarurat hai aur tumhen bashaarat ho aur Allah ke Fazal se achi ho aur aurat iske jawab mein kahey ke tumhari baat maine sun li hai (b-saraahat) koi wada na karey aisi aurat ka wali bhi iske ilm ke baghair koi wada na karey aur agar aurat ne zamana iddat mein kisi mard se nikah ka wada kar liya aur phir baad mein us se nikah kya to donon mein judai nahi karaai jaeygi. Hasan ne kaha ke (لا تواعدوهن سرا) se ye murad hai ke aurat se chhup kar badkaarii na karo. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai ke) الكتاب أجله‏ ( se murad iddat ka pura karna hai.
5125,mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (nikaah se pahley) maine tumhen khuwab mein dekha ke aik farishta (Jibraaiil (al)) resham ke aik tukdey main tumhen lapet kar ley aaya hai aur mujh se keh raha hai ke ye tumhari biwi hai. maine iske chehrey se kapda hataya to wo tum thin. maine kaha ke agar ye khuwab Allah ki taraf se hai to wo usey khud hi pura kar dega.
5126,"aik khatun Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main aap ki khidmat main apne aapko hiba karne aai hun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki taraf dekha aur nazar utha kar dekha, phir nazar neechi kar li aur sar ko jhukaa liya. jab khatun ne dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke barey mein koi faisla nahi farmaya to baith gaiin. iske baad aap ke sahaba mein se aik sahib khadey huey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! agar aapko unki zarurat nahi to unka nikah mujh se kara dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas koi cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi ya rasoolullaah, Allah ki qasam! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apne ghar jao aur dekho shayad koi cheez mil jaey. wo gaey aur wapas aa kar kaha ke nahi ya Rasulullah ! maine koi cheez nahi paai . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur dekh lo, agar aik lohey ki anguthi bhi mil jaey. wo gaey aur wapas aa kar arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mujhey lohey ki anguthi bhi nahi mili , albatta ye mera tahmad hai. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unke paas chadar bhi nahi thi (un sahabi ne kaha ke) un khatun ko us tahmad mein se aadha inayat farma dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye tumharey tahmad ka kya karegi agar tum usey pahnogey to uske liye usmein se kuchh baqi nahi rahega. iske baad wo sahib baith gaey aur der tak baithey rahe phir khadey huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein wapas jatey huey dekha aur unhein bulaney ke liye farmaya, unhein bulaya gaya. jab wo aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke tumharey paas Quran Majeed kitna hai. unhon-ne arz kya falan-falan soortein . unhon-ne un Suraton ko ginaayaa . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum un Suraton ko zabani padh letey ho. unhon-ne haan mein jawab diya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya ke jao maine us khatun ko tumharey nikah mein us Quran ki wjah se diya jo tumharey paas hai. un Suraton ko usey yad kara do."
5127,"aur unhein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki paak bevi Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne khabar di ke zamane jahiliyat mein nikah char tarah hotey they. aik sura to yahi thi jaisey aaj-kal log kartey hain, aik shakhs doosrey shakhs ke paas uski zer parwarish ladki ya uski beti ke nikah ka paigham bhejta aur uska mehar de kar us se nikah kar letaa. doosra nikah ye tha ke koi shauhar apni biwi se jab wo haiz se paak ho jati to kehta to falan shakhs ke paas chali ja aur us se munh kala kara ley us muddat mein shauhar us se juda rehta aur usey chhootaa bhi nahi. phir jab us ghair mard se uska hamal zahir ho jata jis se wo aarizii taur par sohbat karti rahtii, to hamal ke zahir honey ke baad uska shauhar agar chahta to us se sohbat karta. aisa isliye kartey they taake unka ladka sharif aur umda paida ho. ye nikah ''istibzaa'' kahlaataa tha. teesri qism nikah ki ye thi ke chand aadmi jo tadaad mein das se kam hotey kisi aik aurat ke paas aana jana rakhtey aur us se sohbat kartey. phir jab wo aurat haamla hoti aur bachcha jantii to bachcha paida ho janey par chand din guzarney ke baad wo aurat apne un tamam mardon ko bulaatii. us mauqe par unmein se koi shakhs inkar nahi kar sakta tha. chunanche wo sab us aurat ke paas jama ho jatey aur wo unse kehti ke jo tumhara mamla tha wo tumhen malum hai aur ab maine ye bachcha janaa hai. phir wo kehti ke aey fulaan! ye bachcha tumhara hai. wo jiska chahti naam ley deti aur wo ladka usi ka samjha jata, wo shakhs us se inkar ki jur'at nahi kar sakta tha. chotha nikah us taur par tha ke bahut se log kisi aurat ke paas aaya jaya kartey they. aurat apne paas kisi bhi aaney waley ko rokti nahi thi. ye kasbiyaan hoti thin. is tarah ki auratein apne darwazon par jhandey lagaey rehti thin jo nishani samjhey jatey they. jo bhi chahta unke paas jata. is tarah ki aurat jab haamla hoti aur bachcha jantii to uske paas aaney janey waley jama hotey aur kisi qiyaafa jaanney waley ko bulatey aur bachche ka naak-naqsha jisse milta jultaa hota us aurat ke us ladkey ko usi ke sath mansub kar detey aur wo bachcha usi ka betaa kaha jata, us se koi inkar nahi karta tha. phir jab Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haq ke sath rasool ho kar tashrif laey aap ne jahiliyat ke tamam nikaahon ko baatil qarar de diya sirf us nikah ko baqi rakha jiska aaj kal riwaaj hai."
5128,"aayat (وما يتلى عليكم في الكتاب في يتامى Nisa اللاتي لا تؤتونهن ما كتب لهن وترغبون أن تنكحوهن) yaanii ''wo ( aayatein bhi) jo tumhen kitab ke andar un yateem ladkon ke barey mein padh kar sunai jati hain jinhein tum wo nahi detey ho jo unke liye muqarrar ho chuka hai aur us se bezaar ho ke unka kisi se nikah karo.'' aisi yateem ladki ke barey mein nazil hui thi jo kisi shakhs ki parwarish mein ho. mumkin hai ke uske maal w jaaidaad mein bhi Sharik ho, wahi ladki ka zyada haqdaar hai lekin wo us se nikah nahi karna chahta albatta uske maal ki wjah se usey rokey rakhta hai aur kisi doosrey mard se uski shadi nahi honey deta kyonke wo nahi chahta ke koi doosra uske maal mein hisse daar baney."
5129,jab Hafsa binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ibne- Huzafa Sehmi se bewa huin. ibne- Huzafa (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein se they aur badr ki jang mein Sharik they unki wafat Madina Munawra mein hui thi to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unhein pesh kash! ki aur kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main Hafsa ka nikah aap se karun. unhon-ne jawab diya ke main is maamle mein ghaur karunga. chand din maine intizar kya iske baad wo mujh se miley aur kaha ke main is nateeje par pahuncha hun ke abhi nikah na karun. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir main Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unse kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main Hafsa ka nikah aap se karun.
5130,"aayat ( فلا تعضلوهن‏ ( ki tafseer mein bayan kya ke mujh se Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ye aayat mere hi barey mein nazil hui thi maine apni aik behan ka nikah aik shakhs se kar diya tha. us ne usey talaaq de di lekin jab iddat poori hui to wo shakhs ( Abul-Badaah ( meri behan se phir nikah ka paigham lekar aaya. maine us se kaha ke maine tum se iska (apni behan (ka nikah kya usey tumhari biwi banaya aur tumhen izzat di lekin tum ne usey talaaq dedii aur ab phir tum nikah ka paigham lekar aaey ho. hargiz nahi, Allah ki qism ! ab main tumhen kabhi usey nahi doonga . wo shakhs Abul-Badaah kuchh bura aadmi na tha aur aurat bhi iske yahan wapas jana chahti thi isliye Allah Taala ne ye aayat nazil ki) فلا تعضلوهن‏ (ke ''tum aurton ko mat roko '' maine arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! ab main kar doonga . bayan kya ke phir unhon-ne apni behan ka nikah us shakhs se kar diya."
5131,"aayat ( ويستفتونك في Nisa قل الله يفتيكم فيهن‏ ( ''aur aap se aurton ke barey mein masla poochhtey hain, aap keh dijiye ke Allah unke barey main tumhen masla bataataa hai.'' aakhir aayat tak farmaya ke ye aayat yateem ladki ke barey mein nazil hui, jo kisi mard ki parwarish mein ho. wo mard iske maal mein bhi Sharik ho aur us se khud nikah karna chahta ho aur iska nikah kisi doosrey se karna pasand na karta ho ke kahin doosra shakhs iske maal mein hissedaar na bin jaey is gharaz se wo ladki ko rokey rakhey to Allah Taala ne logon ko us se mana kya hai."
5132,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein baithey huey they ke aik khatun aaein aur apne aapko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye pesh kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein nazar neechi uper karke dekha aur koi jawab nahi diya phir aap ke sahaba mein se aik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! unka nikah mujh se kara dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas koi cheez hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke mere paas to kuchh nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke lohey ki anguthi bhi nahi ? unhon-ne arz kya ke lohey ki aik anguthi bhi nahi hai. albatta main apni ye chadar phaad ke aadhi unhein de doonga aur aadhi khud rakhoonga . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi, tumharey paas kuchh Quran bhi hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jao maine tumhara nikah unse us Quran Majeed ki wjah se kya jo tumharey sath hai."
5133,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab unka nikah kya to unki umr chh saal thi aur jab unse sohbat ki to us waqt unki umr nau (9) baras ki thi aur wo nau (9) baras aap ke paas rahiin.
5134,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse nikah kya to unki umr chh saal thi aur jab unse sohbat ki to unki umr nau (9) saal thi. Hisham-bin-Urwa ne kaha ke mujhey khabar di gaee hai ke wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nau (9) saal tak rahiin.
5135,"aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aai aur kaha ke main apne aapko aap ke liye hiba karti hun. phir wo der tak khadi rahi. itney mein aik mard ne kaha ke agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski zarurat na ho to uska nikah mujh se farma dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas unhein mehar mein dene ke liye koi cheez hai? usne kaha ke mere paas is tahmad ke siwa aur kuchh nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum apna ye tahmad usko de doge to tumharey paas pahnney ke liye tahmad bhi nahi rahega. koi aur cheez talash kar lo. us mard ne kaha ke mere paas kuchh bhi nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh to talash karo, aik lohey ki anguthi hi sahii ! usey wo bhi nahi mili to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kya tumharey paas kuchh Quran Majeed hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan ! falan-falan soortein hain, un Suraton ka unhon-ne naam liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir ham ne tera nikah us aurat se un Suraton ke ke badley kya jo tum ko yad hain."
5136,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bewa aurat ka nikah us waqt tak na kya jaey jab tak uski ijazat na li jaey aur kunwari aurat ka nikah us waqt tak na kya jaey jab tak uski ijazat na mil jaey. sahaba ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! kunwari aurat izn kyonkar degi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uski sura ye hai ke wo khamosh reh jaey. ye khamoshi uski marzii samjhii jaeygi.
5137,unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kunwari ladki ( kehtey huey) sharmaatii hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke iska khamosh ho jana hi uski raza mandi hai.
5138,"jo donon Yazeed bin Harisa ke betey hain, unse Khansaa-binte-Khizaam ansariya (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke unke walid ne unka nikah kar diya tha, wo shauhar wali thin, unhein ye nikah manzoor nahi tha, isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin , Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us nikah ko radd kar diya."
5139,Khizaam naam ke aik sahabi ne apni ladki ka nikah kar diya tha. phir pichhli hadis ki tarah bayan kya.
5140,unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se sawal kya ke aey Ummul-Momenin ! is aayat mein kya hukm bayan hua hai? (وإن خفتم أن لا تقسطوا في اليتامى‏) ''aur agar tumhen khof ho ke tum yatimon ke barey mein insaf na kar sakogey.'' ( ما ملكت أيمانكم‏ ( tak. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : mere bhaanjey ! is aayat mein us yateem ladki ka hukm bayan hua hai jo apne wali ki parwarish mein ho aur wali ko uske husn aur uske maal ki wjah se uski taraf tawajjoh ho aur wo uska mehar kam karke us se nikah karna chahta ho to aisey logon ko aisi yateem ladkiyon se nikah se manaahii ki gaee hai siwaey is sura ke ke wo unke mehar ke barey mein insaf karein (aur agar insaf nahi kar saktey to unhein unke siwa dusri aurton se nikah ka hukm diya gaya hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uske baad masla puchha to Allah Taala ne aayat ( ويستفتونك في Nisa ( ''aur aap se aurton ke barey mein poochhtey hain'' se ( وترغبون‏ ( tak nazil ki. Allah Taala ne is aayat mein ye hukm nazil kya ke yateem ladkiyan jab sahib maal aur saahibe-jamaal hoti hain tab to mehar mein kami karke us se nikah karna rishta lagaanaa pasand kartey hain aur jab daulat mandi ya khoobsoortii nahi rakhti us waqt usko chhod kar dusri aurton se nikah kar detey hain (ye kya baat) unko chahiye ke jaisey maal w daulat aur husno-jamaal na honey ki sura mein usko chhod detey hain aisey hi us waqt bhi chhod dein jab wo maaldaar aur khoobsurat ho albatta agar insaf se chalein aur uska pura mehar muqarrar karein to khair nikah kar lein.
5141,"aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur us ne apne aapko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nikah ke liye pesh kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey ab aurat ki zarurat nahi hai. is par aik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! unka nikah mujh se kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mere paas to kuchh bhi nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us aurat ko kuchh do, chahe lohey ki aik anguthi hi sahii . unhon-ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! mere paas kuchh bhi nahi hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha tumhen Quran kitna yad hai? arz kya falan-falan soortein yad hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir maine unhein tumharey nikah mein diya. us Quran ke badley jo tum ko yad hai."
5142,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is se mana farmaya hai ke ham kisi ke bhaaw par bhaaw lagaaein aur kisi shakhs ko apne kisi ( deeni ( bhai ke paighaame-nikaah par paigham bhejein yahan tak ke paigham bhejney wala apna irada badal de ya usey paighaame-nikaah bhejney ki ijazat de dey to jaaiz hai.
5143,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bad-gumaanii se bachtey raho kyonke bad-gumaanii sabse jhooti baat hai (aur logon ke raazon ki) khod kured na kya karo aur na ( logon ki niji baat-cheet ko) kaan laga kar suno , aapas mein dushmanii na paida karo balke bhaaii-bhaaii bin kar raho."
5144,aur koi shakhs apne bhai ke paigham par paigham na bhejey yahan tak ke wo nikah karey ya chhod de.
5145,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke meri beti Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) bewa huin to main Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) se mila aur unse kaha ke agar aap chaahein to main aap ka nikah Azeeza Hafsa binte- umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kar dun. phir kuchh dinon ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke nikah ka paigham bheja iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) mujh se miley aur kaha aap ne jo sura mere samney rakhi thi uska jawab maine sirf is wjah se nahi diya tha ke mujhey malum tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka zikr kya hai. main nahi chahta ke aap ka raaz kholun haan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein chhod detey to main unko qabool kar leta . Shuaib ke sath us hadis ko Yunus bin Yazeed aur Musa-bin-Aqba aur Muhammad-bin abi ateeq ne bhi Zohri se riwayat kya hai.
5146,"2 aadmi Madina ke mashriq ki taraf se aaey, wo musalman ho gaey aur bahut hi behtreen zaban aur andaz mein khutba diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke kuchh taqreerein jaadoo ka asar kartii hain."
5147,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey aur jab main dulhan bana kar bithaai gaee Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar tashrif laey aur mere bistar par baithey isi tarah jaisey tum is waqt mere paas baithey huey ho. phir hamarey yahan ki kuchh ladkiyan daf bajaaney lagiin aur mere bap aur chacha jo jange-badr mein Shahid huey they, unka Marsiya (shok geet) padhney lagiin. itney mein, unmein se aik ladki ne padha, aur ham mein aik Nabi hai jo un baton ki khabar rakhtey hain jo kuchh kal honey wali hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye chhod do. iske siwa jo kuchh tum padh rahi thin wo padho."
5148,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik khatun se aik guthli ke wazan ke barabar ( soney ke mehar par) nikah kya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shadi ki khushi unmein dekhi to unse poochha. unhon-ne arz kya ke maine aik aurat se aik guthli ke barabar nikah kya hai aur Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye riwayat is tarah naql ki hai ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik aurat se. aik guthli ke wazan ke barabar soney par nikah kya tha.
5149,"mein logon ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir tha usmein aik khatun khadi huin aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! main apne aapko aap ke liye hiba karti hun aap ab jo chaahein karein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein koi jawab nahi diya. wo phir khadi hui aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! maine apne aapko aap ke liye hiba kar diya hai aap jo chaahein karein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is martaba bhi koi jawab nahi diya. wo teesri martaba khadi huin aur kaha ke unhon-ne apne aapko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye hiba kar diya, aap jo chaahein karein. iske baad aik sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! unka nikah mujh se kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ke tumharey paas kuchh hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jao aur talash karo aik lohey ki anguthi bhi agar mil jaey ley aao . wo gaey aur talash kya, phir wapas aa kar arz kya ke maine kuchh nahi paya , lohey ki aik anguthi bhi nahi mili . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke tumharey paas kuchh Quran hai? unhon-ne arz kya ke ji haan. mere paas falan-falan soortein hain Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jao maine tumhara nikah unse us Quran par kya jo tum ko yad hai."
5150,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi se farmaya ke nikah kar, chahe lohey ki aik anguthi par hi ho."
5151,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tamam sharton mein wo shartein sabse zyada poori ki janey ke laaiq hain jinke zariey tum ne sharmgaahon ko halal kya hai. yani nikah ki shartein zaroor poori karni hongii.
5152,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi aurat ke liye jaaiz nahi ke apni kisi ( saukan ( behan ki talaaq ki shart isliye lagaey taake uske hisse ka piyala bhi khud undel ley kyonke usey wahi milega jo iske muqaddar mein hoga.
5153,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey to unke uper zard rang ka nishan tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske mutaalliq puchha to unhon-ne bataya ke unhon-ne Ansar ki aik aurat se nikah kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke usey mehar kitna diya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke aik guthli ke barabar sona . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir walima kar chahe aik bakri hi ka ho.
5154,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke sath nikah par da'wate-waleema kiya aur musalmanon ke liye khaney ka intizam kya. ( khaney se faraghat ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif le gaey, jaisa ke nikah ke baad aap ka dastoor tha. phir aap ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) ke hujron mein tashrif ley gaey. aap ne unke liye dua ki aur unhon-ne aap ke liye dua ki. phir aap wapas tashrif laey to 2 sahaba ko dekha (ke abhi baithey huey they) isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) phir tashrif ley gaey. ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke) mujhey poori tarah yad nahi ke maine khud Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di ya kisi aur ne khabar di ke wo donon sahabi bhi chaley gaey hain."
5155,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf par zardi ka nishan dekha to puchha ke ye kya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke maine aik aurat se aik guthli ke wazan ke barabar soney ke mehar par nikah kya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala tumhen barkat de dawat walima kar chahe aik bakri hi ki ho.
5156,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab mujh se shadi ki to meri walida ( umme-Roomaan binte- Aamir ( mere paas aaiin aur mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar ke andar le gain . ghar ke andar qabila Ansar ki auratein maujood thin. unhon-ne ( mujh ko aur meri maan ko) yun dua dii بارك وبارك الله ''Allaah karey tum achi ho tumhara naseeba achchha ho.''
5157,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pichhley nabiyon mein se aik Nabi (yoosha' (Alaihissalam) ya Dawud (Alaihissalam) ( ne jang ki aur) jang se pahley) apni qaum se kaha ke mere sath koi aisa shakhs na chaley jisne kisi nai aurat se shadi ki ho aur uske sath sohbat karne ka irada rakhta ho aur abhi sohbat na ki ho.
5158,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya to unki umr chh saal ki thi aur jab unke sath khilwat ki to unki umr nau (9) saal ki thi aur wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nau (9) saal tak rahen.
5159,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina aur khaibar ke darmyan (raaste mein) teen din tak qiyam kya aur wahan Ummul-Momenin Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khilwat ki. maine musalmanon ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke walima par bulaya lekin us dawat mein roti aur gosht nahi tha. aap ne dastar-khuwaan bichhaaney ka hukm diya aur is par khajoor, paneer aur ghi rakh diya gaya aur yahi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka walima tha. musalmanon ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein (kaha ke) ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se hain ya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein londi hi rakha hai (kyonke wo bhi jang khaibar ke qaidiyon mein se thin. is par kuchh ne kaha ke agar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke liye parda karaaein phir to wo ummahaatul momeneen (nabi ki beeviyon) mein se hain aur agar aap unke liye parda na karaaein to phir wo londi ki haisiyat se hain. jab safar hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye apni sawari par peechhey jagah banai aur logon ke aur unke darmyan parda dalwaayaa ."
5160,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se shadi ki thi. meri walida mere paas aaiin aur tanha mujhey aik ghar mein dakhil kar diya. phir mujhey kisi cheez ne khof nahi dilaya siwaey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ke aap achcha hi mere paas chasht ke waqt aa gaey. aap ne mujh se milaap farmaayaa.
5161,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse (jab unhon-ne shadi ki) farmaya tum ne jhaalar daar chaadrein bhi li hain ya nahi? unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! hamarey paas jhaalar daar chaadrein kahan hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jald hi muyassar ho jaaeingii.
5162,"wo aik dulhan ko aik Ansari mard ke paas le gain to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Aaisha ! tumharey paas daf bajaey wala nahi tha, Ansar ko daf pasand hai."
5163,"Anas (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey samney se bani Rifaa ki masjid mein (jo Basra mein hai) guzrey . maine unse suna wo keh rahe they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qaayda tha aap jab Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar ki taraf se guzartey to unke paas jatey, unko salam kartey (wo aap ki dudh-sharik khala hoti thiin) . phir Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke aik baar aisa hua ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dulhaa they. aap ne Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se nikah kya tha to Umme-Sulaim ( meri maan ( mujh se kehney lagiin us waqt ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh tohfa bhejein to achchha hai. maine kaha munasib hai. unhon-ne khajoor aur ghi aur paneer mila kar aik handi mein halwa banaya aur mere hath mein de kar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bhijwaayaa, main lekar aap ke paas chalaa, jab pahuncha to aap ne farmaya rakh de aur ja kar falan-falan logon ko bula la aap ne unka naam liya aur jo bhi koi tujh ko rastey mein miley usko bula ley. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main aap ke hukm ke muwafiq logon ko dawat dene gaya. lot kar jo aaya to kya dekhta hun ke Sara ghar logon se bharaa hua hai. maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath us halwey par rakhey aur jo Allah ko manzoor tha wo zaban se kaha (barkat ki dua farmaaii). phir das das aadmiyon ko khaney ke liye bulana shuru kya. aap unse farmatey jatey they Allah ka naam lo aur har aik aadmi apne aagey se khaaey. (rakaabii ke beech mein hath na daley ( yahan tak ke sab log kha kar ghar ke bahar chal diye. teen aadmi ghar mein baithey baatein kartey rahe aur mujh ko unke na janey se ranj paida hua (is khayal se ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko takleef hogi) aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon ke hujron par gaey mein bhi aap ke peechhey peechhey gaya phir rastey mein maine aap se kaha ab wo teen aadmi bhi chaley gaey hain. us waqt aap lautey aur) Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke hujrey mein) aaey. main bhi hujrey hi mein tha lekin aap ne mere aur apne beech mein parda daal liya. aap sura Ahzaab ki ye aayat padh rahe they. '' musalmaanon! Nabi ke gharon mein na jaya karo magar jab khaney ke liye tum ko andar aaney ki ijazat di jaey us waqt jao wo bhi aisa theek waqt dekh karke khaney ke pakney ka intizar na karna padey albatta jab bulaey jao to andar aa jao aur khaney se farigh hotey hi chal do. baton mein lag kar wahan baithey na raha karo, aisa karne se paighambar ko takleef hoti thi, usko tum se sharm aati thi (ke tum se kahey ke chaley jaao) Allah Taala haq baat mein nahi sharmaataa .'' abu-Usman (Ja'dii-bin-diinaar) kehtey they ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they."
5164,"unhon-ne (apni bahan) Asma (Raziallahu anha) se aik haar udhaar ley liya tha, rastey mein wo gum ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba mein se kuchh aadmiyon ko usey talash karne ke liye bhejaa. talash kartey huey Namaz ka waqt ho gaya (aur pani nahi tha) isliye unhon-ne wuzu ke baghair Namaz padhi. phir jab wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein wapas huey to aap ke samney ye shikwa kya. is par tayammum ki aayat nazil hui. Usaid-bin-Huzair (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aey Aaisha ! Allah tumhen behtar badla de. Allah ki qasam! jab bhi aap par koi mushkil aan padtii hai to Allah Taala ne tum se usey door kya aur issey bhi badhkar ye ke musalmanon ke liye barkat aur bhalai hui."
5165,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi shakhs apni biwi ke paas ham-bistarii ke liye jab aaey to ye dua padhey باسم الله ، Mina padhi. اللهم جنبني الشيطان ، Mina padhi. وجنب الشيطان ما رزقتنا yaanii main Allah ke naam se shuru karta hun aey Allah ! shaitan ko mujh se door rakh aur shaitan ko us cheez se bhi door rakh jo ( aulad ( hamein to ata kare. phir us arse mein unke liye koi aulad naseeb ho to usey shaitan kabhi nuqsan na pahuncha sakega.
5166,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina Munawra hijrat karke aaey to unki umr das baras ki thi. meri maan aur bahnein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat ke liye mujh ko takeed karti rehti thin. chunanche maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki das baras tak khidmat ki aur jab aap ki wafat hui to main bees baras ka tha. parde ke mutaalliq main sabse zyada jaanney walon mein se hun ke Kab nazil hua. sabse pahley ye hukm us waqt nazil hua tha jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Zainab-binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah ke baad unhein apne ghar laey they, aap unke dulhaa baney they. phir aap ne logon ko (da'wate-waleema par) bulaya. logon ne khana khaya aur chaley gaey. lekin kuchh log unmein se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar main ( khaney ke baad bhi) der tak wahin baithey ( baatein kartey rahe ( aakhir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur bahar tashrif ley gaey. mein bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bahar gaya taake ye log bhi chaley jaaein. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chaltey rahe aur main bhi aap ke sath raha. jab aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ke paas darwazey par aaey to aapko malum hua ke wo log chaley gaey hain. isliye aap wapas tashrif laey aur main bhi aap ke sath aaya. jab aap Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein dakhil huey to dekha ke wo log abhi baithey huey hain aur abhi tak nahi gaey hain. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan se phir wapas tashrif laey aur main bhi aap ke sath wapas aa gaya jab aap Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hujre ke darwazey par pahunchey aur aapko malum hua ke wo log chaley gaey hain to aap phir wapas tashrif laey aur main bhi aap ke sath wapas aaya. ab wo log waqei ja chukey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske baad apne aur mere beech mein parda daal diya aur parde ki aayat nazil hui."
5167,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, unhon-ne qabila Ansar ki aik aurat se shadi ki thi ke mehar kitna diya hai? unhon-ne kaha ke aik guthli ke wazan ke barabar sona aur Humaid se riwayat hai ke maine Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur unhon-ne bayan kya ke jab (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur muhajireen sahaaba) Madina hijrat karke aaey to muhajireen ne Ansar ke yahan qiyam kya Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne Sad-bin-Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan qiyam kya. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke main aapko apna maal taqseem kar doonga aur apni 2 beeviyon mein se aik ko aap ke liye chhod doonga . Abdur-Rehman ne kaha ke Allah aap ke ahal w ayaal aur maal mein barkat de phir wo bazar nikal gaey aur wahan tijarat shuru ki aur paneer aur ghi nafe mein kamaayaa. iske baad shadi ki to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse farmaya ke da'wate-waleema kar chahe aik bakri hi ki ho."
5168,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab (Raziallahu anha) jaisa walima apni beeviyon mein se kisi ka nahi kya, unka walima aap ne aik bakri ka kya tha."
5169,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko aazad kya aur phir unse nikah kya aur unki aazadi ko unka mehar qarar diya aur unka walima maleedey se kya.
5170,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik khatun (Zainab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ( ko nikah karke laey to mujhey bheja aur maine logon ko walima khaney ke liye bulaya.
5171,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unke jaisa apni beeviyon mein se kisi ke liye walima kartey nahi dekha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka walima aik bakri se kya tha.
5172,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni aik biwi ka walima 2 mudd (taqreeban pauney 2 seir) jau se kya tha.
5173,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mein se kisi ko da'wate-waleema par bulaya jaey to usey aana chahiye malum hua ke da'wate-waleema ka qabool karna zaroori hai.
5174,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qaidi ko chhudaao, dawat karne waley ki dawat qabool karo aur bimar ki iyaadat karo."
5175,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein saat (7) kaamon ka hukm diya aur saat (7) kaamon se mana farmaya, hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bimar ki iyaadat , janaaze ke peechhey chalney , chheenkney waley ke jawab dene (yarhamakallaah, yani Allah tum par raham karey kahnaa) qism ko pura karne, mazloom ki madad karne , sab ko salam karne aur dawat karne waley ki dawat qabool karne ka hukm diya tha aur hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ki anguthi pahnney , chandi ke bartan istemal karne , reshamii gaddey , qasiya ( reshamii kapda ( istibraq ( motey resham ka kapda (aur deebaaj (eik reshamii kapda (ke istemal se mana farmaya tha. abu-Awana aur Shebani ne Ashas ki riwayat se lafz ( إفشاء السلام‏ ‏ ) mein abul-Ahwas ki mutabiat (pairavi) ki hai."
5176,"abu-Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni shadi par dawat di, unki dulhan Umme- Usaid Sulaamaa binte- Wahab zaroori jo kaam kaaj kar rahi thin aur wahi dulhan bani thin. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tumhen malum hai unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us mauqe par kya pilaya tha? raat ke waqt unhon-ne kuchh khajoorein pani mein bhigo di thin ( subah ko) jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaney se farigh huey to aapko wahi pilaya ."
5177,waleeme ka wo khana badtareen khana hai jis mein sirf maaldaaron ko uski taraf dawat di jaey aur mohtajon ko na khilaaya jaey aur jisne waleeme ki dawat qabool karne se inkar kya usne Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki.
5178,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mujhey bakri ke khur ki dawat di jaey to main usey bhi qabool karunga aur agar mujhey wo khur bhi hadiye mein diye jayen to main usey qabool karunga .
5179,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is waleeme ki jab tumhen dawat di jaey to qabool karo. bayan kya ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) agar rozey se hotey jab bhi waleeme ki dawat ya kisi dusri dawat mein shirkat kartey they.
5180,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton aur bachchon ko kisi shadi se aatey huey dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khushi ke maarey jaldi se khadey ho gaey aur farmaya : ya Allah ! (tu gawah rah) tum log sab logon se zyada mujh ko mahboob ho.
5181,"unhon-ne aik chhota sa gaddaa khareedaa jis mein tasweerein bani hui thin. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey dekha to darwazey par khadey ho gaey aur andar nahi aaey. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey par narazgi ke aasaar dekh liye aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main Allah aur uske rasool se tauba karti hun, maine kya ghalati ki hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye gaddaa yahan kaisey aaya? bayan kya ke maine arz kya maine hi usey khareedaa hai taake aap is par baithein aur is par tek lagaaein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un tasweeron ke) banaaney walon ko) qiyamat ke din azab diya jaeyga aur unse kaha jaeyga ke jo tum ne tasweer saazii ki hai usey zinda bhi karo? aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jin gharon mein tasweerein hoti hain unmein (rahmat ke) Farishtey nahi aatey ."
5182,"jab abu-Usaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) ne shadi ki to unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aap ke sahaba ko dawat di, us mauqe par khana unki dulhan Umme- Usaid hi ne taiyaar kya tha aur unhon-ne hi mardon ke samney khana rakha. unhon-ne patthar ke aik badey pyaley mein raat ke waqt khajoorein bhigo di thi aur jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaney se farigh huey to unhon-ne hi iska sharbat banaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (tohfe ke taur par) peeney ke liye pesh kya."
5183,"abu-Usaid Saaidi ne apni shadi ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dawat di. us din unki biwi hi sab ki khidmat kar rahi thin, halanke wo dulhan thin biwi ne kaha ya Sehal ne ( rawi ko shak tha) ke tumhen malum hai ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kya taiyaar kya tha? maine aap ke liye aik badey pyaley mein raat ke waqt se khajoor ka sharbat taiyaar kya tha."
5184,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurat misl paslii ke hai, agar tum usey seedha karna chaahogey to tod doge aur agar us se fayda hasil karna chaahogey to uski tedh ke sath hi fayda hasil karogey."
5185,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo shakhs Allah aur qiyamat ke din par eman rakhta ho wo apne padosi ko takleef na pahunchaaey aur main tumhen .) Baqiiya agli hadis dekhein ( .
5186,aurton ke barey mein bhalai ki wasiiyat karta hun kyonke wo paslii se paida ki gaee hain aur paslii mein bhi sabse zyada tedhaa uske uper ka hissa hai. agar tum usey seedha karna chaahogey to usey tod daalogey aur agar usey chhod doge to wo tedhii hi baqi reh jaeygi isliye main tumhen aurton ke barey mein achchhey sulook ki wasiiyat karta hun.
5187,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke waqt mein ham apni beeviyon ke sath guftgu aur bahut zyada be-takallufi se is dar ki wjah se parhez kartey they ke kahin koi be-aitidaalii ho jaey aur hamari burai mein koi hukm nazil na ho jaey. phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee to ham ne unse khub khul ke guftgu ki aur khub be-takallufi karne lagey.
5188,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se har aik Hakim hai aur har aik se ( uski raiyat ke barey mein) sawal hoga. to imam Hakim hai us se sawal hoga. mard apni beewii-bachchon ka Hakim hai aur us se sawal hoga. aurat apne shauhar ke maal ka Hakim hai aur us se sawal hoga. ghulam apne sardaar ke maal ka Hakim hai aur us se sawal hoga haan to tum mein se har aik Hakim hai aur har aik se sawal hoga.
5189,"unhon-ne kaha ke gyara (11) aurton ka aik ijtimaa hua jis mein unhon-ne aapas mein ye tay kya ke majlis mein wo apne apney khawind ka sahi saheeh haal bayan karein, koi baat na chhipaaein. chunanche pehli aurat ( naam naa-maaloom ( bolii mere khawind ki misal aisi hai jaisey dubley oont ka gosht jo pahaad ki choti par rakha hua ho na to wahan tak janey ka rasta saaf hai ke aasani se chadh kar usko koi ley aaey aur na wo gosht hi aisa mota taaza hai jisey laney ke liye us pahaad par chadhney ki takleef gawara kare. doosrii aurat ( Umra binte- Amr tamimi naam ke) kehney lagi main apne khawind ka haal bayan karun to kahan tak bayan karun (us mein itney aib hain) main dartii hun ke sab bayan na kar sakoongii is par bhi agar bayan karun to uske khuley aur chhipey sarey aib bayan kar sakti hoon. teesrii aurat (huyii binte- Kab Yamani ( kehney lagi , mera khawind kya hai aik taad ka taad ( lambaa-tadangaa ( hai agar uske aib bayan karun to talaaq taiyaar hai agar khamosh rahoon to idhar latkii rahoon . chothi aurat (Mehdu-binte-abii-Harooma) kehney lagi ke mera khawind mulk tahaama ki raat ki tarah moa'tadil na zyada garm na bahut thanda na us se mujh ko khof hai na uktaahat hai. paanchwiin aurat (Kabsha naamii) kehney lagi ke mera khawind aisa hai ke ghar mein aata hai to wo aik cheetaa hai aur jab bahar nikalta hai to sher ( bahaadur ( ki tarah hai. jo cheez ghar mein chhod kar jata hai uske barey mein poochhta hi nahi (ke wo kahan gaee ? ( itna be-parwaah hai jo aaj kamaayaa usey kal ke liye utha kar rakhta hi nahi itna data hai. chhatii aurat ( Hind naam ke) kehney lagi ke mera khawind jab khaney par aata hai to sab kuchh chat kar jata hai aur jab peeney par aata hai to aik boond bhi baqi nahi chhorta aur jab let'taa hai to tanha hi apne uper kapda lapet leta hai aur alag pad kar so jata hai mere kapdey mein kabhi hath bhi nahi daalta ke kabhi mera dukh dard kuchh to malum kare. saatwiin aurat ( huyii binte- Alqama ( mera khawind to jaahi ya mast hai. sohbat ke waqt apna Sina mere seeney se aundha pad jata hai. duniya mein jitney aib logon mein eik-eik karke jama hain wo sab uski zaat mein jama hain (kam bakht se baat karun to ( sar phod daley ya hath tod daley ya donon kaam kar daley . aathwiin aurat (Yaasir binte-aos) kehney lagi mera khawind chhooney mein khargosh ki tarah narm hai aur khushbu mein soongho to zafran jaisa khushbu daar hai. naween aurat ( naam naa-maaloom ( kehney lagi ke mere khawind ka ghar bahut uncha aur buland hai wo qadaawar bahaadur hai, uske yahan khana is qadr paktaa hai ke raakh ke dher ke dher jama hain. ( ghareebon ko khub khilata hai) log jahan salaah w mashwara ke liye baithtey hain (yani panchaayat ghar ( wahan se iska ghar bahut nazdeek hai. dasween aurat ( Kabsha binte- Raafe ( kehney lagi mere khawind ka kya poochhna jaaidaad wala hai, jaaidaad bhi kaisi badi jaaidaad waisii kisi ke paas nahi ho sakti bahut sarey oont jo jaa-bajaa uske ghar ke paas jutey rahtey hain aur jangal mein charney kam jatey hain. jahan un oonton ne baajey ki awaz suni bas unko apne zabah honey ka yaqin ho gaya. gyaarahwiin aurat (umme-zara' binte- Ukaimil-binte-Saaida) kehney lagi mera khawind abu-Zara' hai uska kya kehna us ne mere kanon ko zewaron se bojhal kar diya hai aur mere donon bazu charbi se phulaa diye hain mujhey khub khilaa kar mota kar diya hai ke main bhi apne taiin khub motii samajhney lagi hun. shadi se pahley mein thodi se bhed-bakriyon mein tangi se guzar-Basar karti thi. Abu-Zaraa ne mujh ko ghodon, oonton, khet khaliyiaan sab ka Malik bana diya hai itni bahut jaaidaad milney par bhi uska mizaaj itna umda hai ke baat kahun to bura nahi maantaa mujh ko kabhi bura nahi kehta . soii padi rahoon to subah tak mujhey koi nahi jagaataa. pani piyun to khub sairaab ho kar pi loon rahi Abu-Zaraa ki maan ( meri saas ( to main uski kya khubiyan bayan karun. uska khane-pine ka saman khana maal w asbaab se bharaa hua, iska ghar bahut hi kushaada . Abu-Zaraa ka betaa wo bhi kaisa achchha khoobsurat ( naazuk badan dublaa patlaa ( harii chhaalii ya nangii talwaar ke barabar iske soney ki jagah aisa kam khuraak ke bakri ke char maah ke bachchey ka dast ka gosht iska pet bhar de. Abu-Zaraa ki beti wo bhi Subhan-Allah kya kehna apne bap ki pyari , apni maa ki pyari ( taabea' farman itaat guzaar ( kapda bharpur pahnney wali) motii taazii ( saukan ki jalan. Abu-Zaraa ki londi uski bhi kya poochhtey ho kabhi koi baat hamari mashhoor nahi karti ( ghar ka bhed hamesha posheeda rakhti hai) khaney tak nahi churaatii ghar mein koodaa-kachraa nahi chhodtii magar aik din aisa hua ke log makkhan nikalney ko doodh math rahe they. ( subah hi subah ( Abu-Zaraa bahar gaya achcha us ne aik aurat dekhi jiske 2 bachchey cheeton ki tarah uski kamar ke taley 2 anaaron se khel rahe they ( murad uski donon chhaatiyaan hain jo anaar ki tarah thiin). Abu-Zaraa ne mujh ko talaaq de kar us aurat se nikah kar liya. uske baad maine aik aur sharif sardaar se nikah kar liya jo ghodey ka achchha sawaar, umda neza baaz hai, usne bhi mujh ko bahut se janwar de diye hain aur har qism ke asbaab mein se eik-eik joda diya hua hai aur mujh se kaha karta hai ke Umme- zara' ! khub kha pi , apne azeez w aqrabaa ko bhi khub khilaa pilaa terey liye aam ijazat hai magar ye sab kuchh bhi jo maine tujh ko diya hua hai agar ikattha karun to terey pahley khawind Abu-Zaraa ne jo tujh ko diya tha, usmein ka aik chhota bartan bhi na bharey."
5190,"kuchh fauji khel ka neza bazi se muzaahira kar rahe they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (apne jism Mubarak se) mere liye parda kya aur main wo khel dekhti rahi. maine usey der tak dekha aur khud hi uktaa kar lot aai. ab tum khud samajh lo ke aik kam Umr ladki khel ko kitni der tak dekh sakti hai aur is mein dilchaspi ley sakti hai."
5191,"bahut dinon tak mere dil mein khahish rahi ke main umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki un 2 beeviyon ke mutaalliq poochhoon jinke barey mein Allah ne ye aayat nazil ki thi. ( إن تتوبا إلى الله فقد صغت قلوبكما‏ ( . aik martaba unhon-ne Haj kya aur unke sath maine bhi Haj kya. aik jagah jab wo raaste se hat kar (qazaaey haajat ke liye) gaey to main bhi aik bartan mein pani lekar unke sath raaste se hat gaya. phir unhon-ne qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ki aur wapas aaey to maine unke hathon par pani dala. phir unhon-ne wuzu kya to maine us waqt unse puchha ke ya ameerul-momineen! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon mein wo kon hain jinke mutaalliq Allah ne ye irshad farmaya ke) إن تتوبا إلى الله فقد صغت قلوبكما‏ ( umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha aey Ibne-Abbas ! tum par hairat hai. wo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) hain phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne tafseel ke sath hadis bayan karni shuru ki. unhon-ne kaha ke main aur mere aik Ansari padosi jo banu- Umayya bin Zaid se they aur awaalii Madina mein rahtey they. ham ne ( awaalii se) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir honey ke liye baari muqarrar kar rakhi thi. aik din wo haziri detey aur aik din mein haziri deta , jab main hazir hota to us din ki tamam khabrein jo wahi wghaira se mutaalliq hotiin laataa (aur apne padosi se bayan karta (aur jis din wo hazir hotey to wo bhi aisey kartey. ham qureshi log apni aurton par ghalib they lekin jab ham Madina tashrif laey to ye log aisey they ke aurton se maghloob they, hamari aurton ne bhi Ansar ki aurton ka tariqa seekhnaa shuru kar diya. aik din maine apni biwi ko daantaa to usne bhi mera turkii-b-turkii jawab diya. maine uske is tarah jawab deney par na-gawari ka izhar kya to usne kaha ke mera jawab dena tumhen bura kyon lagta hai, Allah ki qism ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan bhi unko jawabaat de deti hain aur kuchh to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik din raat tak alag rehti hain. main is baat par kanp utha aur kaha ke unmein se jisne bhi ye mamla kya yaqinan wo naa-muraad ho gaee. phir maine apne kapdey pahney aur (Madina ke liye) rawaana hua phir main Hafsa ke ghar gaya aur maine us se kaha : aey Hafsa ! kya tum mein se koi bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se eik-eik din raat tak ghussa rehti hai? unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan kabhi (aisaa ho jata hai) maine is par kaha ke phir tum ne apne aapko khasaare mein daal liya aur naa-muraad hui. kya tumhen iska koi dar nahi ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghussa ki wjah se Allah tum par ghussa ho jaey aur phir tum tanha hi ho jaaogii . khabardaar ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mataalbaat (maangein) na kya karo na kisi maamle main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jawab diya karo aur na Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chhoda karo. agar tumhen koi zarurat ho to mujh se maang liya karo. tumhari saukan jo tum se zyada khoobsurat hai aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tum se zyada pyari hai, unki wjah se tum kisi ghalat-fahmii mein na mubtala ho jaanaa. unka ishara Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf tha. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke hamein malum hua tha ke mulk ghassaan ham par hamla ke liye fauji taiyaariyaan kar raha hai. mere Ansari sathi apni baari par Madina Munawra gaey huey they. wo raat gaey wapas aaey aur mere darwazey par badi zor-zor se dastak di aur kaha ke kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) ghar mein hain. main ghabraa kar bahar nikla to unhon-ne kaha ke aaj to bada haadisa ho gaya. maine kaha kya baat hui, kya ghassaanii chadh aaey hain? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi, haadisa us se bhi bada aur us se bhi zyada khofnak hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paak beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai. maine kaha ke Hafsa to ghaatey mein chali gayi aur naa-muraad hui. mujhey to iska khatrah laga hi rehta tha ke is tarah ka koi haadisa jald hi hoga phir maine apne tamam kapdey pahney (aur Madina ke liye rawaana ho gaya) maine fajr ki Namaz Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhi (namaz ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne aik bula khaane mein chaley gaey aur wahan tanhai ikhtiyar kar li. main Hafsa ke paas gaya to wo ro rahi thi. maine kaha ab roti kya ho. maine tumhen pahley hi khabardaar kar diya tha. kya Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen talaaq de di hai? unhon-ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt bula khaane mein tanha tashrif rakhtey hain. main wahan se nikla aur member ke paas aaya. iske gird kuchh sahaba kiram maujood they aur unmein se kuchh ro rahe they. thodi der tak main unke sath betha raha. iske baad mera gham mujh par ghalib aa gaya aur main us bula khaane ke paas aaya. jahan Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif rakhtey they. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik habshi ghulam se kaha ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye andar aaney ki ijazat ley lo. ghulam andar gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se guftgu karke wapas aa gaya. us ne mujh se kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ka zikr kya lekin aap khamosh rahe. chunanche main wapas chala aaya aur phir un logon ke sath baith gaya jo member ke paas maujood they. mera gham mujh par ghalib aaya aur dobara aa kar maine ghulam se kaha ke umr ke liye ijazat ley lo. us ghulam ne wapas aa kar phir kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aap ka zikr kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh rahe. main phir wapas aa gaya aur member ke paas jo log maujood they unke sath baith gaya. lekin mera gham mujh par ghalib aaya aur maine phir aa kar ghulam se kaha ke umr ke liye ijazat talab karo. ghulam andar gaya aur wapas aa kar jawab diya ke maine aap ka zikr Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh rahe. mein wahan se wapas aa raha tha ke ghulam ne mujh ko pukara aur kaha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tumhen ijazat de di hai. main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aap us baan ki charpai par jis se chatai bunii jati hai letey huey they. is par koi bistar nahi tha. baan ke nishanat aap ke pahlu Mubarak par padey huey they. jis takiye par aap tek lagaey huey they usmein chhaal bhari hui thi. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko salam kya aur khadey hi khadey arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri taraf nigaah uthai aur farmaya nahi. main ( khushi ki wjah se) keh utha . Allahu-akbar . phir maine khadey hi khadey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khush karne ke liye kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aapko malum hai ham Quraish ke log aurton par ghalib raha kartey they. phir jab ham Madina aaey to yahan ke logon par unki auratein ghalib thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par muskuraa diye. phir maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aapko malum hai main Hafsa ke paas aik martaba gaya tha aur us se keh aaya tha ke apni saukan ki wjah se jo tum se zyada khoobsurat aur tum se zyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko azeez hai, dhoke mein mat rehna. unka ishara Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf tha. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dobara muskuraa diye. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko muskuratey dekha to baith gaya phir nazar utha kar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar ka jaaiza liya. Allah ki qism ! maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghar mein koi aisi cheez nahi dekhi jis par nazar ruktii. siwa teen chamdon ke (jo wahan maujood they) maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! Allah se dua farmaein ke wo aap ki ummat ko faraakhii ata farmaaey. Faaris w Rome (mojooda Itly) ko faraakhii aur wusat hasil hai aur unhein duniya di gaee hai halanke wo Allah ki ibadat nahi kartey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abhi tak tek lagaey huey they lekin ab seedhey baith gaey aur farmaya : ibne-khattaab ! tumhari nazar mein bhi ye cheezein ahmiyat rakhti hain, ye to wo log hain jinhein jo kuchh bhalai milney wali thi sab isi duniya mein de di gaee hai. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere liye Allah se maghfirat ki dua kar dijiye (ke maine duniyawi shaan w shaukat ke mutaalliq ye ghalat khayal dil mein rakhaa) chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ko isi wjah se untees din tak alag rakha ke Hafsa ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka raaz Aaisha se keh diya tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke aik maheene tak main apni beeviyon ke paas nahi jaaunga. kyonke jab Allah Taala ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par itaab kya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iska bahut ranj hua (aur aap ne beeviyon se alag rehney ka faisla kya) phir jab untiswin raat guzar gaee to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar tashrif le gaey aur aap se shuruaat ki. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ne qism khaaii thi ke hamarey yahan aik mahina tak tashrif nahi laaengey aur abhi to untees hi din guzrey hain main to eik-eik din gin rahi thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye mahina untees ka hai. wo mahina untees hi ka tha. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Allah Taala ne aayat (takhyeer : beevi ko is baat ka ikhtiyar diya jaana ki wo chahe to shauhar ke sath rahe aur na chahey to na rahey) nazil ki aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni tamam beeviyon mein sabse pahley mere paas tashrif laey (aur mujh se Allah ki wahi ka zikr kya ( to maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hi pasand kya. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni tamam dusri beeviyon ko ikhtiyar diya aur sab ne wahi kaha jo Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) keh chuki thin."
5192,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar shauhar ghar par maujood hai to koi aurat uski ijazat ke baghair ( nafli ( roza na rakhey .
5193,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab shauhar apni biwi ko apne bistar par bulaey aur wo aaney se ( narazagi ki wjah se) inkar kar de to Farishtey subah tak is par laanat bhejtey hain.
5194,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar aurat apne shauhar se narazagi ki wjah se iske bistar se alag-thalag raat guzarney to Farishtey is par us waqt tak laanat bhejtey hain jab tak wo apni us harkat se baaz na aa jaey.
5195,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurat ke liye jaaiz nahi ke apne shauhar ki maujoodgii mein uski ijazat ke baghair ( nafli ( roza rakhey aur aurat kisi ko iske ghar mein uski marzii ke baghair aaney ki ijazat na de aur aurat jo kuchh bhi apne shauhar ke maal mein se uski sareeh ijazat ke baghair kharch kar de to usey bhi iska aadha sawab milega. is hadis ko abu-Zinaad ne Musa bin abi Usman se bhi aur unse unke walid ne aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kya hai aur is mein sirf roze ka hi zikr hai.
5196,mein jannat ke darwaze par khada hua to usmein dakhil honey walon ki aksariyat ghareebon ki thi. maaldaar (jannat ke darwazey par hisab ke liye) rok liye gaey they albatta jahannam walon ko jahannam mein janey ka hukm de diya gaya tha aur main jahannam ke darwazey par khada hua to usmein dakhil honey wali zyada auratein thin.
5197,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein suraj girahan hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ke sath uski Namaz padhi. aap ne bahut lamba qiyam ki itna lamba ke sura al-Baqara padhi ja sakey phir lamba rukoo kya. rukoo se sar utha kar bahut der tak qiyam kya. ye qiyam pahley qiyam se kuchh kam tha. phir aap ne doosra lamba rukoo kya. ye rukoo tawaalat mein pahley rukoo se kuchh kam tha. phir sar uthaya aur sajda kya. phir dobara qiyam kya aur bahut der tak haalate-qiyaam mein rahe. ye qiyam pehli rakaat ke qiyam se kuchh kam tha. phir lamba rukoo kya, ye rukoo pahley rukoo se kuchh kam lamba tha. phir sar uthaya aur lamba qiyam kya. ye qiyam pahley qiyam se kuchh kam tha. phir rukoo kya, lamba rukoo aur ye rukoo pahley rukoo se kuchh kam lamba tha. phir sar uthaya aur sajde mein gaey. jab aap Namaz se farigh huey to girahan khatm ho chuka tha. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke suraj aur chaand Allah ki nishaniyon mein se do nishaniyan hain. unmein girahan kisi ki maut ya kisi ki hayaat ki wjah se nahi hota. isliye jab tum girahan dekho to Allah ko yad karo. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ne aapko dekha ke aap ne apni jagah se koi cheez badh kar li. phir ham ne dekha ke aap ham se hat gaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine jannat dekhi thi ya (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya rawi ko shak tha) mujhey jannat dikhai gaee thi. maine iska khosha todney ke liye hath badhaya tha aur agar main usey tod leta to tum rehti duniya tak usey khaatey aur maine dozakh dekhi aaj ka us se zyada haibat naak manzar maine kabhi nahi dekha aur maine dekha ke usmein aurton ki tadaad zyada hai. sahaba ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aisa kyon hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo shauhar ki na-shukri karti hain aur unke ehsan ka inkar karti hain, agar tum unmein se kisi aik ke sath zindagi bhar bhi husne-sulook ka mamla karo phir bhi tumhari taraf se koi cheez uske liye naa-gawaare-khaatir hui to keh degi ke maine to tum se kabhi bhalai dekhi hi nahi."
5198,maine jannat mein jhank kar dekha to iske aksar rehney waley ghareeb log they aur maine dozakh mein jhank kar dekha to iske andar rehney wali aksar auratein thin. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Abu-Ayub aur Salam bin Zareer ne ki hai.
5199,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Abdullah ! kya meri ye itlaa sahi hai ke tum ( rozaana ( din mein rozey rakhtey ho aur raat bhar ibadat kartey ho? maine arz kya : ji haan ya Rasulullah ! Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aisa na karo, rozey bhi rakho aur baghair rozey bhi raho. raat mein ibadat bhi karo aur so'o bhii. kyonke tumharey badan ka bhi tum par haq hai, tumhari aankh ka bhi tum par haq hai aur tumhari biwi ka bhi tum par haq hai."
5200,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein se har aik Hakim hai aur har aik se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga. ameer ( Hakim ( hai, mard apne ghar walon par Hakim hai. aurat apne shauhar ke ghar aur uske bachchon par Hakim hai. tum mein se har aik Hakim hai aur har aik se uski raiyat ke barey mein sawal hoga."
5201,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni paak beeviyon se aik mahina tak alag rahe aur apne aik baalaakhaane mein qiyam kya. phir aap untees din ke baad ghar mein tashrif laey to kaha gaya ke ya Rasulullah ! aap ne to aik mahina ke liye ahad kya tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye mahina untees ( 29 (ka hai.
5202,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik waaqie ki wjah se) qism khaaii ke apni kuchh beeviyon ke yahan aik mahina tak nahi jaengey. phir jab untees din guzar gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas subah ke waqt gaey ya Sham ke waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya gaya ke aap ne to qism khaaii thi ke aik mahina tak nahi aaeingey ? aap ne farmaya ke mahina untees din ka bhi hota hai.
5203,"ham se Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke aik din subah hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyan ro rahi thin, har paak bevi ke paas unke ghar waley maujood they. masjid ki taraf gaya to wo bhi logon se bhari hui thi. phir umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein uper gaey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt aik kamre mein tashrif rakhtey they. unhon-ne salam kya lekin kisi ne jawab nahi diya. unhon-ne phir salam kya lekin kisi ne jawab nahi diya. phir salam kya aur is martaba bhi kisi ne jawab nahi diya. to awaz di (ba'd mein ijazat milney par) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gaey aur arz kya : kya aap ne apni beeviyon ko talaaq de di hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi balke aik maheene tak unse alag rehney ki qism khaaii hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) untees din tak alag rahe aur phir apne beeviyon ke paas gaey."
5204,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum mein koi shakhs apni biwi ko ghulaamon ki tarah na maarey ke phir doosrey din us se ham-bistar hoga.
5205,"qabila Ansar ki aik khatun ne apni beti ki shadi ki thi. iske baad ladki ke sar ke baal bimari ki wjah se ud gaey to wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur aap se iska zikr kya aur kaha ke iske shauhar ne is se kaha hai ke apne baalon ke sath (doosrey masnooii baal ( jodey . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke aisa to hargiz mat kar, kyonke masnooii baal sar par rakh ke jo jodey to aisey baal jodney waaliyon par laanat ki gaee hai."
5206,"aayat وإن امرأة خافت من بعلها نشوزا أو إعراضا ''aur agar koi aurat apne shauhar ki taraf se nafrat aur munh modney ka khof mehsus kare. '' ke mutaalliq farmaya ke aayat mein aisi aurat ka bayan hai jo kisi mard ke paas ho aur wo mard usey apne paas zyada na bulata ho balke usey talaaq dene ka irada rakhta ho aur uske bajaey dusri aurat se shadi karna chahta ho lekin uski maujooda biwi us se kahey ke mujhey apne sath hi rakho aur talaaq na do. tum mere siwa kisi aur se shadi kar saktey ho, mere kharch se bhi tum aazad ho aur tum par baari ki bhi koi pabandi nahi to uska zikr Allah Taala ke is irshad mein) فلا جناح عليهما أن يصالحا بينهما صلحا والصلح (ke '' to un par koi gunah nahi agar wo aapas mein suleh kar lein aur suleh bahar-haal behtar hai.''"
5207,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein ham azl kya kartey they.
5208,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein jab Quran nazil ho raha tha ham azl kartey they.
5209,Quran nazil ho raha tha aur ham azl kartey they.
5210,(eik jang mein) hamein qaidi auratein miliin aur ham ne unse azl kya. phir ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska hukm puchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tum waqei aisa kartey ho? teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ( phir farmaya ( qiyamat tak jo Rooh bhi paida honey wali hai wo (apne waqt par) paida ho kar rahegi . to tumhara azl karna bekaar ki harkat hai.
5211,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab safar ka irada kartey to apni beeviyon ke liye Qura daaltey. aik martaba Qura Aaisha aur Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke naam nikla . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat ke waqt ma'moolan chaltey waqt Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke sath baatein kartey huey chaltey . aik martaba Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha ke aaj raat kyon na tum mere oont par Sawar ho jao aur main tumharey oont par taake tum bhi naey munaazir dekh sako aur main bhii. unhon-ne ye tajwiz qabool kar li aur (har aik doosrey ke oont par) Sawar ho gain . uske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha ke oont ke paas tashrif laey. us waqt is par Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) baithi hui thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein salam kya, phir chaltey rahe, jab padao hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko malum hua ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) usmein nahi hain (is ghalati par Aaisha ko is darje ranj hua ke) jab log sawaariyon se utar gaey to Ummul-Momenin ne apne paon izkhir ghaas mein daal liye aur dua karne lagi ke aey mere rab! mujh par koi bichho ya sanp musallat kar de jo mujh ko das ley. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se to kuchh keh nahi sakti thi kyonke ye harkat khud meri hi thi."
5212,Sauda-binte-Zama ne apni baari Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko de di thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan khud unki baari ke din aur Sauda (Raziallahu anha) ki baari ke din rahtey they.
5213,agar main chaahoon to keh sakta hun ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( aaney wali hadis) irshad farmai . lekin bayan kya ke dastoor ye hai ke jab kunwari se shadi karey to iske sath saat (7) din tak rehna chahiye aur jab bewa se shadi karey to iske sath teen din tak rehna chahiye
5214,"jab koi shakhs pahley se shaadii-shuda biwi ki maujoodgii mein kisi kunwari aurat se shadi karey to uske sath saat (7) din tak qiyam karey aur phir baari muqarrar karey aur jab kisi kunwari biwi ki maujoodgii mein pahley se shadi shuda aurat se nikah karey to iske sath teen din tak qiyam karey aur phir baari muqarrar kare. abu-Qilaba ne bayan kya ke agar main chaahoon to keh sakta hun ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan bayan ki hai. aur Abdur-Razzaq ne bayan kya, unhein Sufiyan ne khabar di, unhein Ayub aur Khalid ne kaha ke agar main chaahoon to keh sakta hun ke Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye hadis Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan bayan ki hai."
5215,aik raat main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni tamam paak beeviyon ke paas gaey. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nikah mein nau (9) beeviyan thin.
5216,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Asr ki Namaz se farigh ho kar apni paak beeviyon ke paas tashrif ley jatey aur unmein se kisi aik ke qareeb bhi baithtey . aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan gaey aur mamool (routine) se zyada kafi der tak thahrey rahe.
5217,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jis marz mein wafat hui, usmein aap puchha kartey they ke kal meri baari kis ke yahan hai? kal meri baari kis ke yahan hai? aapko Aaisha ki baari ka intizar tha. chunanche aap ki tamam beeviyon ne aapko uski ijazat de di ke aap jahan chaahein bimari ke din guzaarein . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar aagey aur yahin aap ki wafat hui. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki isi din wafat hui jo meri baari ka din tha aur Allah Taala ka ye bhi ehsan dekho us ne jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne yahan bulaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak mere seeney par tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke munh ka luaab mere munh ke luaab se mila."
5218,"betii, apni us saukan ko dekh kar dhokey mein na aa jana jisey apne husn par aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mohabbat par naaz hai. aap ka ishara Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf tha ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya (ke phir maine yahi baat aap ke samney dohraaii aap muskuraa diye."
5219,aik khatun ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri saukan hai agar apne shauhar ki taraf se un chizon ke hasil honey ki bhi daastanein usey sunaun jo haqiqat mein mera shauhar mujhey nahi deta to kya usmein koi harj hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke jo cheez hasil na ho is par fakhr karne wala us shakhs jaisa hai jo faraib ka joda yani ( dusron ke kapdey ( maang kar pahney .
5220,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala se zyada ghairat mand aur koi nahi hai. yahi wjah hai ke usne be-hayai ke kaamon ko haram kya hai aur Allah se badh kar koi apni tareef pasand karne wala nahi hai.
5221,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aey ummate-Muhammad ! Allah se badh kar ghairat mand aur koi nahi ke wo apne bandey ya bandi ko zina kartey huey dekhey. aey ummate-Muhammad ! agar tumhen wo malum hota jo mujhey malum hai to tum hanstey kam aur rotey zyada .
5222,"unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke Allah Taala se zyada ghairat mand koi nahi aur (isii sanad se) Yahya se riwayat hai ke unse abu-Salma ne bayan kya aur unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna."
5223,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ko ghairat aati hai aur Allah Taala ko ghairat us waqt aati hai jab bandae-momin wo kaam karey jisey Allah ne haram kya hai.
5224,"Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se shadi ki to unke paas aik oont aur unke ghodey ke siwa poori zameen par koi maal, koi ghulaam, koi cheez nahi thi. main hi unka ghoda charaatii, pani pilaatii, unka dol seetii aur aata goondhtii . main achi tarah roti nahi pakka sakti thi. Ansar ki kuchh ladkiyan meri roti pakka jati thin. ye badi sachchii aur baa-wafaa auratein thin. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki wo zameen jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein di thi, us se main apne sar par khajoor ki guthliyaan ghar laya karti thi. ye zameen mere ghar se 2 meel door thi. aik roz mein aa rahi thi aur guthliyaan mere sar par thin ke rastey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat ho gaee. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath qabila Ansar ke kai aadmi they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya phir (apne oont ko bithaaney ke liye) kaha akh-akh. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chahtey they ke mujhey apni sawari par apne peechhey sawar kar lein lekin mujhey mardon ke sath chalney mein sharm aai aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ki ghairat ka bhi khayal aaya. Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) badey hi baa-ghairat they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi samajh gaey ke main sharm mehsus kar rahi hun. isliye aap aagey badh gaey. phir main Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aai aur unse waqia ka zikr kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se meri mulaqat ho gaee thi. mere sar par guthliyaan thin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aap ke chand sahaba bhi they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna oont mujhey bithaaney ke liye bithaya lekin mujhey us se sharm aai aur tumhari ghairat ka bhi khayal aaya. is par Zuber ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! mujh ko to us se bada ranj hua ke to guthliyaan laney ke liye nikley agar to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sawar ho jati to itni ghairat ki baat na thi (kyonke Asma (Raziallahu anha) aap ki saalii aur bhaawaj donon hoti thiin) iske baad mere walid Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik ghulam mere paas bhej diya wo ghodey ka sab kaam karne laga aur main be-fikr ho gaee maano walid maajid Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ghulaam bhej kar) mujh ko aazad kar diya."
5225,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni aik bevi ( Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) (ke yahan tashrif rakhtey they. us waqt aik bevi ( Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ( ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye aik pyaley mein kuchh khaney ki cheez bheji jinke ghar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt tashrif rakhtey they. unhon-ne khaadim ke hath par (ghusse mein) maara jiski wjah se katora gir kar toot gaya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne katora lekar tukdey jama kiye aur jo khana us bartan mein tha usey bhi jama karne lagey aur (khaadim se) farmaya ke tumhari maan ko ghairat aa gaee hai. iske baad khaadim ko rokey rakha. aakhir jinke ghar mein wo katora tootaa tha unki taraf se nayaa katora mangaya gaya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo nayaa katora un paak bevi ko wapas kya jinka katora tod diya gaya tha aur tootaa hua katora unke yahan rakh liya jinke ghar mein wo tootaa tha.
5226,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main jannat mein dakhil hua ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) mein jannat mein gaya, wahan maine aik mahal dekha maine puchha ye mahal kis ka hai? farishton ne bataya ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kaa. maine chaha ke uske andar jaun lekin ruk gaya kyonke tumhari ghairat mujhey malum thi. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere maan-baap aap par fidaa hun, aey Allah ke Nabi ! kya main aap par ghairat karunga."
5227,ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baithey huey they Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khuwab mein maine apne aapko jannat mein dekha. wahan maine dekha ke aik mahal ke kinarey aik aurat wuzu kar rahi thi. maine puchha ke ye mahal kis ka hai? Farishtey ne kaha ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) kaa. main unki ghairat ka khayal karke wapas chala aaya. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo us waqt majlis mein maujood they is par ro diye aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya main aap par ghairat karunga ?
5228,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya ke main khub pehchanta hun ke Kab tum mujh se khush hoti ho aur Kab tum mujh par naraz ho jati ho. bayan kya ke is par maine arz kya aap ye baat kis tarah samajhtey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum mujh se khush hoti ho to kehti ho nahi Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke rab ki qism ! aur jab tum mujh se naraz hoti ho to kehti ho nahi Ibrahim ke rab ki qism ! bayan kya ke maine arz kya ji haan , Allah ki qism ya Rasulullah ! ( ghussey mein) sirf aap ka naam zaban se nahi leti ."
5229,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kisi aurat par mujhey itni ghairat nahi aati thi jitni Ummul-Momenin Khadija (Raziallahu anha) par aati thi kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka zikr kasrat se kya kartey they aur unki tareef kartey they aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi ki gaee thi ke aap Khadija ko jannat mein unke mautaa ke ghar ki bashaarat de dein.
5230,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mimber par farma rahe they ke Hisham bin Mughira jo abu-Jahal ka bap tha uski aulad ( Haris-bin-Hisham aur Salam bin Hisham ( ne apni beti ka nikah Ali-bin abi-Talib se karne ki mujh se ijazat mangi hai lekin main unhein hargiz ijazat nahi doonga yaqinan main uski ijazat nahi doonga hargiz main uski ijazat nahi doonga . albatta agar Ali-bin abi-Talib meri beti ko talaaq de kar unki beti se nikah karna chaahein (to mein usmein rukawat nahi banoonga ( kyonke wo ( Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ( mere jigar ka aik tukda hai jo usko bura lagey wo mujh ko bhi bura lagta hai aur jis cheez se usey takleef pahunchti hai us se mujhey bhi takleef pahunchti hai."
5231,"main tum se wo hadis bayan karunga jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai, mere siwa ye hadis tum se koi aur nahi bayan karne wala hai. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke qiyamat ki nishaniyon mein se ye bhi hai ke Quran w hadis ka ilm utha liya jaeyga aur jahaalat badh jaeygi. zina ki kasarat ho jaeygi aur sharab log zyada peeney lagengey. mard kam ho jaeinge aur aurton ki tadaad zyada ho jaeygi. haalat ye ho jaeygi ke pachaas pachaas aurton ka sanbhaalney wala ( khabar geer ( aik mard hoga."
5232,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aurton mein janey se bachtey raho is par qabila Ansar ke aik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! dewar ke mutaalliq aap ki kya raey hai? (wo apni bhaawaj ke sath ja sakta hai ya nahin?) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke dewar ya ( jeth (ka jana hi to halaakat hai.
5233,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ke siwa koi mard kisi aurat ke sath tanhai mein na baithey. is par aik sahabi ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! meri biwi Haj karne gaee hai aur mera naam falan jang mein likha gaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir to wapas ja aur apni biwi ke sath Haj kar.
5234,qabila Ansar ki aik khatun Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaiin aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se logon se aik taraf ho kar tanhai mein guftgu ki iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log (yani Ansar ( mujhey sab logon se zyada azeez ho.
5235,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahan tashrif rakhtey they, ghar mein aik mughees naam ke mukhannas bhi tha. us mukhannas ( heejdey ( ne Umme-Salma ke bhai Abdullah-bin-Ubai Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke agar kal Allah ne tumhen Taaif par fateh inayat farmai to main tumhen Ghelaan ki beti ko dikhlaaunga kyonke wo samney aati hai to ( mutaapey ki wjah se) uske char shiknein pad jati hain aur jab peechhey phirtii hai to aath (8) ho jati hain. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Umme-Salma se) farmaya ke ye ( mukhannas ( tumharey paas ab na aaya kare."
5236,"maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere liye apni chadar se parda kiye huey hain. main Habsha ke un logon ko dekh rahi thi jo masjid main ( jangi ( khel ka muzaahira kar rahe they, aakhir mein hi uktaa gaee. ab tum samajh lo aik kam Umr ladki jis ko khel tamasha dekhney ka bada shauq hai kitni der tak dekhti rahi hogi."
5237,"Ummul-Momenin Sauda-binte-Zama (Raziallahu anhu) raat ke waqt bahar niklin to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein dekh liya aur pehchan gaey. phir kaha : aey Sauda , Allah ki qism ! tum ham se chhup nahi saktin . jab Sauda (Raziallahu anha) wapas Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaein to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iska zikr kya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt mere hujrey mein Sham ka khana kha rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein gosht ki aik haddi thi. us waqt aap par wahi nazil honii shuru hui aur jab nuzool wahi ka silsile khatm hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhen ijazat di gaee hai ke tum apni zarooriyaat ke liye bahar nikal sakti ho."
5238,jab tum mein se kisi ki biwi masjid mein (namaz padhney ke liye) janey ki ijazat maangey to usey na roko balke ijazat de do.
5239,"mere dudh-sharik chacha (aflah) aaey aur mere paas andar aaney ki ijazat chahi lekin maine kaha ke jab tak main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochh na loon, ijazat nahi de sakti . phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine aap se iske mutaalliq poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo tumharey dudh-sharik chacha hain, unhein andar bula lo. maine is par kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! aurat ne mujhey doodh pilaya tha koi mard ne thoda hi pilaya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hain to wo tumharey chacha hi (doodh-shareek) isliye wo tumharey paas aa saktey hain, ye waqia hamarey liye parde ka hukm nazil honey ke baad ka hai. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke khoon se jo cheezein haram hoti hain doodh pilaaney se bhi wo haram ho jati hain."
5240,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi aurat kisi aurat se milney ke baad apne shauhar se uska huliya na bayan karey, maano ke wo usey dekh raha hai."
5241,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi aurat kisi aurat se mil kar apne shauhar se iske huliya na bayan karey maano ke wo usey dekh raha hai.
5242,Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (al) ne farmaya ke aaj raat main apni so beeviyon ke paas ho aaoonga (aur us qurbat ke nateeje mein) har aurat aik ladka janegi to so ladkey aisey paida hongey jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad karengey. farishta ne unse kaha ke inshaAllah keh lijiye lekin unhon-ne nahi kaha aur bhool gaey. chunanche aap tamam beeviyon ke paas gaey lekin aik ke siwa kisi ke bhi bachcha paida na hua aur us aik ke yahan bhi aadha bachcha paida hua. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar inshaAllah keh letey to unki murad bar aati aur unki khahish poori honey ki ummeed zyada hoti.
5243,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi shakhs se raat ke waqt apne ghar (safar se achcha ( aaney par na-pasandidgi ka izhar farmatey they.
5244,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar tum mein se koi shakhs zyada dinon tak apne ghar se door ho to yakaayak raat ko apne ghar mein na aa jaey.
5245,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jihad ( jange-Tabook ( mein tha, jab ham wapas ho rahe they, to main apne sust raftaar oont ko tez chalaney ki koshish kar raha tha. itney mein mere peechhey se aik sawar mere qareeb aaey. maine mud kar dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jaldi kyon kar rahe ho? maine arz kya ke meri shadi abhi nai hui hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, kunwari aurat se tum ne shadi ki ya bewa se ? maine arz kya ke bewa se. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya, kunwari se kyon na ki? tum iske sath kheltey aur wo tumharey sath kheltii . Jaabir ne bayan kya ke phir jab ham Madina pahunchey to ham ne chaha ke Shahar mein dakhil ho jayen lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thahar jao . raat ho jaey phir dakhil hona taake tumhari beeviyan jo paraaganda baal hain wo kanghi choti kar lein aur jinke khawind ghayab they wo naaf ke nichey ke baal saaf kar lein. Hushaim ne bayan kya ke mujh se aik moa'tabar rawi ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi farmaya ke aey Jaabir! jab to ghar pahunchey to khub khoob ( كيس ( kiijiyo (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ( ) كيس (ka matlab hai ke aulad honey ki khahish kiijiyo ."
5246,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jange-Tabook se waapsii ke waqt) farmaya, jab raat ke waqt tum Madina mein pahuncho to us waqt tak apne gharon mein na jana jab tak unki beeviyan jo Madina Munawra mein maujood nahi they, apney naaf ke nichey ke baal saaf na kar lein aur jinke baal paraa bikhrey huey wo kangha na kar lein. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir zaroori hai ke jab tum ghar pahuncho to khub khoob ( كيس ( kiijiyo . Shabi ke sath us hadis ko Ubaidullah ne bhi Wahab bin kaisaan se, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kya, usmein bhi) كيس (ka zikr hai."
5247,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang (jange-Tabook) mein they. wapas hotey huey jab ham Madina Munawra ke qareeb pahunchey to maine apne sust raftaar oont ko tez chalaney laga. aik sahib ne peechhey se mere qareeb pahunch kar mere oont ko aik chhadi se jo unke paas thi, maara . us se oont badi achi chaal chalney laga, jaisa ke tum ne achchhey oonton ko chaltey huey dekha hoga. maine mud kar dekha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) they. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! meri nai shadi hui hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par poochha, kya tum ne shadi kar li ? maine arz kya ke ji haan. malum farmaya, kunwari se ki hai ya bewa se ? bayan kya ke maine arz kya ke bewa se ki hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kunwari se kyon na ki? tum uske sath kheltey aur wo tumharey sath kheltii . bayan kya ke phir jab ham Madina pahunchey to Shahar mein dakhil honey lagey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke thahar jao raat ho jaey phir dakhil hona taake bikhrey huey baalon wali aurat choti kangha kar ley aur jiska shauhar maujood na raha ho wo naaf ke nichey ke baal saaf kar ley."
5248,"is waqia mein logon mein ikhtilaf tha ke Uhud ki jang ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye kon si dawaa istemal ki gaee thi. phir logon ne Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kya, wo us waqt aakhiri sahabi they jo Madina Munawra mein maujood they. unhon-ne batlaya ke ab koi shakhs aisa zinda nahi jo us waqia ko mujh se zyada janta ho. Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehre se khoon dho rahi thin aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apne dhaal mein pani bhar kar la rahe they. (jab band na hua to) aik boriyaa jalaa kar aap ke zakhm mein bhar diya gaya."
5249,"tum Baaqar eid ya eid ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath maujood they? unhon-ne kaha ke haan. agar main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka rishtedar na hota to main apni kam-umrii ki wjah se aisey mauqe par hazir nahi ho sakta tha. unka ishara (is zamaney mein) apne bachpan ki taraf tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif le gaey aur) logon ke sath eid ki) Namaz padhi aur uske baad khutba diya. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne azan aur iqamat ka zikr nahi kya, phir aap aurton ke paas aaey aur unhein waz (nasihat) w nasihat ki aur unhein khairat dene ka hukm diya. maine unhein dekha ke phir wo apne kanon aur galey ki taraf hath badhaa-badhaa kar (apne zewaraat) Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko dene lagiin. iske baad Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas tashrif laey."
5250,(unke waalid) Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) un par ghussa huey aur meri kokh mein hath se kachokey lagaaney lagey lekin main harkat is wjah se na kar saki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka sar Mubarak meri raan par rakha hua tha.
